#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/optimize/utilize_activities.rst:139
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Schedule` field, choose a default deadline for these "
"activities. To do so, configure a desired number "
"of :guilabel:`Days`, :guilabel:`Weeks`, or :guilabel:`Months`. Then, decide "
"if it should occur :guilabel:`after completion date` or :guilabel:`after "
"previous activity deadline`."
