#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma.rst:3
msgid "Pro-forma invoices"
msgstr "Счета-проформы"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma.rst:5
msgid ""
"A *pro-forma invoice* is an abridged or estimated invoice sent in advance of "
"a delivery of goods. It notes the kind and quantity of goods, their value, "
"and other important information, such as weight and transportation charges."
msgstr ""
"*Счет-проформа* — это сокращенный или предварительный счет, отправляемый до "
"доставки товара. В нем указывается вид и количество товара, его стоимость и "
"другая важная информация, такая как вес и транспортные расходы."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma.rst:9
msgid ""
"Pro-forma invoices are commonly used as preliminary invoices with a "
"quotation. They are also used during importation for customs purposes. They "
"differ from a normal invoice, in that they are *not* a demand (or request) "
"for payment."
msgstr ""
"Счета-проформы обычно используются в качестве предварительных счетов вместе "
"с коммерческим предложением. Они также используются при импорте в таможенных "
"целях. Они отличаются от обычного счета тем, что *не* являются требованием "
"(или запросом) об оплате."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma.rst:16
msgid ""
"In order to utilize pro-forma invoices, the *Pro-Forma Invoice* feature "
"**must** be activated."
msgstr ""
"Чтобы использовать счета-проформы, функция *Счет-проформа* **должна** быть "
"активирована."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma.rst:18
msgid ""
"To enable this feature, navigate to :menuselection:`Sales app --> "
"Configuration --> Settings`, and in the :guilabel:`Quotations \\& Orders` "
"section, click the checkbox next to :guilabel:`Pro-Forma Invoice`. Then, "
"click :guilabel:`Save` to save all changes."
msgstr ""
"Чтобы включить эту функцию, перейдите в :menuselection:`Приложение «Продажи"
"» --> Настройка --> Настройки`, и в разделе :guilabel:`Коммерческие "
"предложения и заказы` установите флажок рядом с :guilabel:`Счет-проформа`. "
"Затем нажмите :guilabel:`Сохранить`, чтобы сохранить все изменения."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma.rst:None
msgid "The Pro-Forma Invoice feature setting in the Odoo Sales application."
msgstr "Настройка функции «Счет-проформа» в приложении Odoo «Продажи»."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma.rst:27
msgid "Send pro-forma invoice"
msgstr "Отправка счета-проформы"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma.rst:29
msgid ""
"With the :guilabel:`Pro-Forma Invoice` feature activated, the option to send "
"a pro-forma invoice is now available on any quotation or sales order, via "
"the :guilabel:`Send Pro-Forma Invoice` button."
msgstr ""
"При активированной функции :guilabel:`Счет-проформа` возможность отправки "
"счета-проформы теперь доступна для любого коммерческого предложения или "
"заказа на продажу с помощью кнопки :guilabel:`Отправить счет-проформу`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma.rst:None
msgid ""
"The Send Pro-Forma Invoice button on a typical sales order in Odoo Sales."
msgstr ""
"Кнопка «Отправить счет-проформу» в типичном заказе на продажу в Odoo «Продажи"
"»."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma.rst:37
msgid ""
"Pro-forma invoices can **not** be sent for a sales order or quotation if an "
"invoice for a down payment has already been sent, or for a recurring "
"subscription."
msgstr ""
"Счета-проформы **не могут** быть отправлены для заказа на продажу или "
"коммерческого предложения, если счет на авансовый платеж уже был отправлен, "
"или для регулярной подписки."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma.rst:40
msgid ""
"In either case, the :guilabel:`Send Pro-Froma Invoice` button does **not** "
"appear."
msgstr ""
"В любом из этих случаев кнопка :guilabel:`Отправить проформу счёта` **не** "
"отображается."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma.rst:42
msgid ""
"However, pro-forma invoices **can** be sent for services, event "
"registrations, courses, and/or new subscriptions. Pro-forma invoices are not "
"limited to physical, consumable, or storable goods."
msgstr ""
"Однако проформы счетов **могут** быть отправлены для услуг, регистраций на "
"мероприятия, курсов и/или новых подписок. Проформы счетов не ограничиваются "
"физическими, расходными или складскими товарами."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma.rst:45
msgid ""
"When the :guilabel:`Send Pro-Forma Invoice` button is clicked, a pop-up "
"window appears, from which an email can be sent."
msgstr ""
"При нажатии кнопки :guilabel:`Отправить проформу счёта` появляется "
"всплывающее окно, из которого можно отправить электронное письмо."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma.rst:48
msgid ""
"In the pop-up window, the :guilabel:`Recipients` field is auto-populated "
"with the customer from the sales order or quotation. The :guilabel:`Subject` "
"field and the body of the email can be modified, if necessary."
msgstr ""
"Во всплывающем окне поле :guilabel:`Получатели` автоматически заполняется "
"клиентом из заказа на продажу или коммерческого предложения. Поле "
":guilabel:`Тема` и текст письма можно изменить при необходимости."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma.rst:52
msgid ""
"The pro-forma invoice is automatically added as an attachment to the email."
msgstr "Проформа счёта автоматически добавляется в качестве вложения к письму."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma.rst:54
msgid ""
"When ready, click :guilabel:`Send`, and Odoo instantly sends the email, with "
"the attached pro-forma invoice, to the customer."
msgstr ""
"Когда всё готово, нажмите :guilabel:`Отправить`, и Odoo мгновенно отправит "
"письмо с приложенной проформой счёта клиенту."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma.rst:None
msgid ""
"The email pop-up window that appears with pro-forma invoice attached in Odoo "
"Sales."
msgstr ""
"Всплывающее окно электронного письма с приложенной проформой счёта в Odoo "
"Продажи."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma.rst:62
msgid ""
"To preview what the pro-forma invoice looks like, click on the PDF at the "
"bottom of the email pop-up window *before* clicking :guilabel:`Send`. When "
"clicked, the pro-forma invoice is downloaded instantly. Open that PDF to "
"view (and review) the pro-forma invoice."
msgstr ""
"Чтобы просмотреть, как выглядит проформа счёта, нажмите на PDF-файл в нижней "
"части всплывающего окна электронного письма *перед* нажатием "
":guilabel:`Отправить`. При нажатии проформа счёта загружается мгновенно. "
"Откройте этот PDF-файл для просмотра (и проверки) проформы счёта."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma.rst:0
msgid "Sample pro-forma invoice PDF from Odoo Sales."
msgstr "Образец PDF-файла проформы счёта из Odoo Продажи."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:3
msgid "Invoicing based on time and materials"
msgstr "Выставление счетов на основе времени и материалов"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:5
msgid ""
"Invoicing based on time and/or materials is typically used when accurately "
"estimating the size of a project isn't possible, or when the requirements of "
"a project may change."
msgstr ""
"Выставление счетов на основе времени и/или материалов обычно используется, "
"когда точная оценка масштаба проекта невозможна или когда требования проекта "
"могут измениться."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:8
msgid ""
"This is different from a fixed-price contract, when a customer agrees to pay "
"a specified total for the fulfillment of the contract---no matter what needs "
"to be paid to the employees, sub-contractors, vendors, suppliers, and so on."
msgstr ""
"Это отличается от контракта с фиксированной ценой, когда клиент соглашается "
"заплатить определённую сумму за выполнение контракта — независимо от того, "
"что необходимо заплатить сотрудникам, субподрядчикам, поставщикам и так "
"далее."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:12
msgid ""
"The Odoo *Sales* app can invoice for time and various other expenses (e.g. "
"transport, lodging), as well as purchases needed to fulfill an order."
msgstr ""
"Приложение Odoo *Продажи* может выставлять счета за время и различные другие "
"расходы (например, транспорт, проживание), а также за покупки, необходимые "
"для выполнения заказа."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:16
msgid "App and settings configuration"
msgstr "Конфигурация приложения и настроек"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:18
msgid ""
"First, in order to accurately keep track of the progress of a project, the "
"Odoo *Project* and *Accounting* apps **must** be installed."
msgstr ""
"Во-первых, для точного отслеживания хода выполнения проекта **должны** быть "
"установлены приложения Odoo *Проект* и *Бухгалтерский учёт*."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:21
msgid ""
"To install the *Project* app, navigate to :menuselection:`Odoo main "
"dashboard --> Apps`. Then, on the :guilabel:`Apps` page, locate "
"the :guilabel:`Project` app block, and click :guilabel:`Activate`. The page "
"automatically refreshes and returns to the main Odoo dashboard, where the "
"*Project* app is now available to access."
msgstr ""
"Чтобы установить приложение *Проект*, перейдите в :menuselection:`Главная "
"панель Odoo --> Приложения`. Затем на странице :guilabel:`Приложения` "
"найдите блок приложения :guilabel:`Проект` и нажмите "
":guilabel:`Активировать`. Страница автоматически обновится и вернётся к "
"главной панели Odoo, где приложение *Проект* теперь доступно."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:26
msgid "Repeat the same process to install the *Accounting* application."
msgstr "Повторите тот же процесс для установки приложения *Бухгалтерский учёт*."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:28
msgid ""
"After installation, click the :guilabel:`Accounting` app icon from the main "
"Odoo dashboard, and navigate to :menuselection:`Configuration --> Settings`. "
"On the :guilabel:`Settings` page, scroll down to the :guilabel:`Analytics` "
"section, and ensure the box next to :guilabel:`Analytic Accounting` is "
"checked."
msgstr ""
"После установки нажмите на значок приложения :guilabel:`Бухгалтерский учёт` "
"на главной панели Odoo и перейдите в :menuselection:`Конфигурация --> "
"Настройки`. На странице :guilabel:`Настройки` прокрутите вниз до раздела "
":guilabel:`Аналитика` и убедитесь, что установлен флажок рядом с "
":guilabel:`Аналитический учёт`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:None
msgid ""
"How it looks to activate the Analytic Accounting setting in Odoo Accounting "
"Setting page."
msgstr ""
"Как выглядит активация настройки Аналитический учёт на странице настроек "
"Odoo Бухгалтерский учёт."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:37
#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:43
msgid "Then, click :guilabel:`Save` to save all changes."
msgstr "Затем нажмите :guilabel:`Сохранить`, чтобы сохранить все изменения."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:39
msgid ""
"Then, navigate to :menuselection:`Odoo main dashboard --> Project app --> "
"Configuration --> Settings`. On the :guilabel:`Settings` page, in "
"the :guilabel:`Time Management` section, ensure the box beside "
"the :guilabel:`Timesheets` feature is checked."
msgstr ""
"Затем перейдите в :menuselection:`Главная панель управления Odoo --> "
"Приложение Проект --> Настройка --> Настройки`. На странице "
":guilabel:`Настройки`, в разделе :guilabel:`Управление временем`, убедитесь, "
"что установлен флажок рядом с функцией :guilabel:`Табели`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:None
msgid ""
"What the Timesheets feature looks like on the Odoo Project settings page."
msgstr ""
"Как выглядит функция Табели на странице настроек приложения Проект в Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:52
msgid "Service product configuration"
msgstr "Настройка продукта-услуги"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:54
msgid ""
"With the *Timesheets* feature activated in the *Project* app, it is now "
"possible to invoice for time spent on a project, but **only** when the "
"following product configurations have been made."
msgstr ""
"После активации функции *Табели* в приложении *Проект* появляется "
"возможность выставлять счета за время, затраченное на проект, но **только** "
"при выполнении следующих настроек продукта."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:58
msgid ""
"Invoicing for time spent on a project is **only** possible with products "
"that have *Service* set as the *Product Type* on their product form."
msgstr ""
"Выставление счетов за время, затраченное на проект, возможно **только** для "
"продуктов, у которых в форме продукта в качестве *Типа продукта* установлено "
"значение *Услуга*."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:61
msgid ""
"To configure a service product, first navigate to :menuselection:`Sales app "
"--> Products --> Products`. On the :guilabel:`Products` page, select the "
"desired service product to be configured, or click :guilabel:`New` to create "
"a new product."
msgstr ""
"Чтобы настроить продукт-услугу, сначала перейдите в "
":menuselection:`Приложение Продажи --> Продукты --> Продукты`. На странице "
":guilabel:`Продукты` выберите нужный продукт-услугу для настройки или "
"нажмите :guilabel:`Создать`, чтобы создать новый продукт."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:65
msgid ""
"From the product form, in the :guilabel:`General Information` tab, set "
"the :guilabel:`Product Type` to :guilabel:`Service`. Then, open the drop-"
"down menu in the :guilabel:`Invoicing Policy` field, and "
"select :guilabel:`Based on Timesheets`."
msgstr ""
"В форме продукта на вкладке :guilabel:`Общая информация` установите "
":guilabel:`Тип продукта` как :guilabel:`Услуга`. Затем откройте "
"раскрывающееся меню в поле :guilabel:`Политика выставления счетов` и "
"выберите :guilabel:`На основе табелей`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:69
msgid ""
"Next, from the :guilabel:`Create on Order` drop-down menu, "
"select :guilabel:`Project \\& Task`. That setting indicates that, when a "
"sales order is created with this specific service product, a new project and "
"task is created in the *Project* app."
msgstr ""
"Далее в раскрывающемся меню :guilabel:`Создать при заказе` выберите "
":guilabel:`Проект и задача`. Эта настройка означает, что при создании заказа "
"на продажу с этим конкретным продуктом-услугой в приложении *Проект* "
"создаются новый проект и задача."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:None
msgid ""
"The correct settings for Invoicing Policy and Create on Order fields for "
"service product."
msgstr ""
"Правильные настройки полей Политика выставления счетов и Создать при заказе "
"для продукта-услуги."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:78
msgid ""
"The option :guilabel:`Task` can be chosen instead from the :guilabel:`Create "
"on Order` drop-down menu. If :guilabel:`Task` is chosen, select an existing "
"project that the task will appear in from :guilabel:`Project` field, which "
"only appears if :guilabel:`Task` is chosen in the :guilabel:`Create on "
"Order` field."
msgstr ""
"Вместо этого в раскрывающемся меню :guilabel:`Создать при заказе` можно "
"выбрать вариант :guilabel:`Задача`. Если выбрана :guilabel:`Задача`, "
"выберите существующий проект, в котором появится задача, в поле "
":guilabel:`Проект`, которое отображается, только если в поле "
":guilabel:`Создать при заказе` выбрана :guilabel:`Задача`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:84
msgid "Add time spent to sales order"
msgstr "Добавление затраченного времени в заказ на продажу"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:86
msgid ""
"After properly configuring a service product with the correct *Invoicing "
"Policy* and *Create on Order* options, it is possible to add time spent to a "
"sales order."
msgstr ""
"После правильной настройки продукта-услуги с корректными параметрами "
"*Политика выставления счетов* и *Создать при заказе* появляется возможность "
"добавлять затраченное время в заказ на продажу."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:89
msgid ""
"To see that in action, navigate to :menuselection:`Sales app --> New` to "
"open a blank quotation form. Then, proceed to add a :guilabel:`Customer`, "
"and in the :guilabel:`Order Lines` tab, click :guilabel:`Add a product`, and "
"select the properly :ref:`configured service product <sales/invoicing/"
"configured-service-product>` from the drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
"Чтобы увидеть это в действии, перейдите в :menuselection:`Приложение "
"Продажи --> Создать`, чтобы открыть пустую форму коммерческого предложения. "
"Затем добавьте :guilabel:`Клиента`, и на вкладке :guilabel:`Позиции заказа` "
"нажмите :guilabel:`Добавить продукт` и выберите правильно :ref:`настроенный "
"продукт-услугу <sales/invoicing/configured-service-product>` из "
"раскрывающегося меню."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:94
msgid "Next, click :guilabel:`Confirm` to confirm the order."
msgstr "Далее нажмите :guilabel:`Подтвердить`, чтобы подтвердить заказ."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:96
msgid ""
"After confirming the sales order, two smart buttons appear at the top of the "
"order form: :guilabel:`Projects` and :guilabel:`Tasks`."
msgstr ""
"После подтверждения заказа на продажу в верхней части формы заказа "
"появляются две умные кнопки: :guilabel:`Проекты` и :guilabel:`Задачи`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:None
msgid ""
"How the Projects and Tasks smart buttons look on a Sales Order in Odoo Sales."
msgstr ""
"Как выглядят умные кнопки Проекты и Задачи в заказе на продажу в приложении "
"Продажи Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:103
msgid ""
"If the :guilabel:`Projects` smart button is clicked, it reveals the specific "
"project related to this sales order. If the :guilabel:`Tasks` smart button "
"is clicked, it reveals the specific project task related to this sales "
"order. Both are also accessible in the *Project* app."
msgstr ""
"Если нажать умную кнопку :guilabel:`Проекты`, откроется конкретный проект, "
"связанный с этим заказом на продажу. Если нажать умную кнопку "
":guilabel:`Задачи`, откроется конкретная задача проекта, связанная с этим "
"заказом на продажу. Оба элемента также доступны в приложении *Проект*."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:107
msgid ""
"In order to add time spent on a sales order, click the :guilabel:`Tasks` "
"smart button."
msgstr ""
"Чтобы добавить затраченное время в заказ на продажу, нажмите умную кнопку "
":guilabel:`Задачи`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:109
msgid ""
"On the task form, select the :guilabel:`Timesheets` tab. From "
"the :guilabel:`Timesheets` tab, employees can be assigned to work on the "
"project, and the time they spend working on the task can be added by the "
"employees or by the person who created the sales order."
msgstr ""
"В форме задачи выберите вкладку :guilabel:`Табели`. На вкладке "
":guilabel:`Табели` можно назначить сотрудников для работы над проектом, а "
"время, которое они тратят на работу над задачей, может быть добавлено "
"сотрудниками или лицом, создавшим заказ на продажу."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:113
msgid ""
"To add an employee, and the time spent working on the task, "
"click :guilabel:`Add a line` in the :guilabel:`Timesheets` tab. Then, select "
"the appropriate :guilabel:`Date` and :guilabel:`Employee`. There is also the "
"option to add a brief description of the work done during this time in "
"the :guilabel:`Description` column, but it's not required."
msgstr ""
"Чтобы добавить сотрудника и время, затраченное на работу над задачей, "
"нажмите :guilabel:`Добавить строку` на вкладке :guilabel:`Табели`. Затем "
"выберите соответствующие :guilabel:`Дату` и :guilabel:`Сотрудника`. Также "
"есть возможность добавить краткое описание работы, выполненной за это время, "
"в столбце :guilabel:`Описание`, но это не обязательно."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:118
msgid ""
"Lastly, enter the amount of time worked on the task in the :guilabel:`Hours "
"Spent` column, and click away to complete that line in "
"the :guilabel:`Timesheets` tab."
msgstr ""
"Наконец, введите количество времени, потраченного на задачу, в столбце "
":guilabel:`Затраченные часы` и щелкните в стороне, чтобы завершить эту "
"строку на вкладке :guilabel:`Табели`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:122
msgid ""
"The time entered in the :guilabel:`Hours Spent` column is immediately "
"reflected in the :guilabel:`Allocated Time` field (located near the top of "
"the task form) as a percentage, which reflects how much of the total "
"allocated work hours have been done so far."
msgstr ""
"Время, введенное в столбце :guilabel:`Затраченные часы`, немедленно "
"отражается в поле :guilabel:`Выделенное время` (расположено в верхней части "
"формы задачи) в процентах, что показывает, сколько из общего количества "
"выделенных рабочих часов уже выполнено."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:126
msgid ""
"That same information is found as numerical hours in the :guilabel:`Hours "
"Spent` and :guilabel:`Remaining Hours` fields, located at the bottom of "
"the :guilabel:`Timesheets` tab."
msgstr ""
"Та же информация представлена в числовых часах в полях "
":guilabel:`Затраченные часы` и :guilabel:`Оставшиеся часы`, расположенных "
"внизу вкладки :guilabel:`Табели`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:0
msgid ""
"How the Timesheets tab appears on a task form in Odoo Sales and Odoo Project."
msgstr ""
"Как выглядит вкладка Табели в форме задачи в Odoo Продажи и Odoo Проект."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:133
msgid ""
"Repeat this process for however many employees and hours have been worked on "
"the project."
msgstr ""
"Повторите этот процесс для любого количества сотрудников и часов, "
"отработанных над проектом."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:136
msgid "Invoice time spent"
msgstr "Выставление счета за затраченное время"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:138
msgid ""
"Once all the necessary employees and time spent have been added to the "
"project task, return to the sales order to invoice the customer for those "
"hours. To do that, either click the :guilabel:`Sales Order` smart button at "
"the top of the task form, or return to the sales order via the breadcrumb "
"links, located in the upper-left of the screen."
msgstr ""
"После того как все необходимые сотрудники и затраченное время были добавлены "
"в задачу проекта, вернитесь к заказу на продажу, чтобы выставить счет "
"клиенту за эти часы. Для этого либо нажмите смарт-кнопку :guilabel:`Заказ на "
"продажу` в верхней части формы задачи, либо вернитесь к заказу на продажу "
"через ссылки навигации, расположенные в верхнем левом углу экрана."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:143
msgid ""
"Back on the sales order form, the time that was added to the task is "
"reflected in the :guilabel:`Order Lines` tab (in the :guilabel:`Delivered` "
"column) and in the new :guilabel:`Recorded Hours` smart button at the top of "
"the sales order."
msgstr ""
"В форме заказа на продажу время, добавленное к задаче, отражается на вкладке "
":guilabel:`Строки заказа` (в столбце :guilabel:`Доставлено`) и в новой смарт-"
"кнопке :guilabel:`Зарегистрированные часы` в верхней части заказа на продажу."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:147
msgid ""
"To invoice the customer for time spent on the project, "
"click :guilabel:`Create Invoice`, and select :guilabel:`Regular invoice` "
"from the :guilabel:`Create invoices` pop-up window. Then, "
"click :guilabel:`Create Draft Invoice`."
msgstr ""
"Чтобы выставить счет клиенту за время, потраченное на проект, нажмите "
":guilabel:`Создать счет` и выберите :guilabel:`Обычный счет` во всплывающем "
"окне :guilabel:`Создать счета`. Затем нажмите :guilabel:`Создать черновик "
"счета`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:151
msgid ""
"Doing so reveals a :guilabel:`Customer Invoice Draft`, clearly showing all "
"the work that's been done in the :guilabel:`Invoice Lines` tab."
msgstr ""
"Это откроет :guilabel:`Черновик счета клиента`, четко показывающий всю "
"выполненную работу на вкладке :guilabel:`Строки счета`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:155
msgid ""
"Pay attention to the :guilabel:`Analytic Distribution` column in "
"the :guilabel:`Customer Invoice`, as that information is necessary to ensure "
"other time/material invoicing tasks are completed properly and accurately."
msgstr ""
"Обратите внимание на столбец :guilabel:`Аналитическое распределение` в "
":guilabel:`Счете клиента`, поскольку эта информация необходима для "
"правильного и точного выполнения других задач выставления счетов за время/"
"материалы."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:0
msgid "Invoice draft showing time spent on sales order in Odoo Sales."
msgstr ""
"Черновик счета, показывающий время, потраченное на заказ на продажу, в Odoo "
"Продажи."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:163
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Confirm` to confirm the invoice and continue with the "
"invoicing process."
msgstr ""
"Нажмите :guilabel:`Подтвердить`, чтобы подтвердить счет и продолжить процесс "
"выставления счетов."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:169
msgid "Expenses configuration"
msgstr "Настройка расходов"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:171
msgid ""
"In order to track and invoice expenses related to a sales order, the Odoo "
"*Expenses* app **must** be installed."
msgstr ""
"Чтобы отслеживать и выставлять счета за расходы, связанные с заказом на "
"продажу, **необходимо** установить приложение Odoo *Расходы*."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:174
msgid ""
"To install the *Expenses* app, navigate to :menuselection:`Odoo main "
"dashboard --> Apps`. Then, on the :guilabel:`Apps` page, locate "
"the :guilabel:`Expenses` app block, and click :guilabel:`Activate`."
msgstr ""
"Чтобы установить приложение *Расходы*, перейдите в :menuselection:`Главная "
"панель управления Odoo --> Приложения`. Затем на странице "
":guilabel:`Приложения` найдите блок приложения :guilabel:`Расходы` и нажмите "
":guilabel:`Активировать`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:178
msgid ""
"The page automatically refreshes and returns to the main Odoo dashboard, "
"where the :guilabel:`Expenses` app is now available to access."
msgstr ""
"Страница автоматически обновится и вернется к главной панели управления "
"Odoo, где приложение :guilabel:`Расходы` теперь доступно для использования."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:184
msgid "Add expenses to sales order"
msgstr "Добавление расходов к заказу на продажу"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:186
msgid ""
"To add an expense to a sales order, first navigate to "
"the :menuselection:`Expenses` app. Then, from the main *Expenses* dashboard, "
"click :guilabel:`New`, which reveals a blank expense form."
msgstr ""
"Чтобы добавить расход к заказу на продажу, сначала перейдите в приложение "
":menuselection:`Расходы`. Затем на главной панели управления *Расходы* "
"нажмите :guilabel:`Создать`, что откроет пустую форму расхода."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:189
msgid ""
"On the expense form, add a :guilabel:`Description` of the expense (e.g. "
"`Hotel Stay`, `Plane Ticket`). Next, in the :guilabel:`Category` field, "
"select the appropriate option from the drop-down menu "
"(e.g. :guilabel:`Meals`, :guilabel:`Miles`, :guilabel:`Travel \\& "
"Accommodation`)."
msgstr ""
"В форме расхода добавьте :guilabel:`Описание` расхода (например, `Проживание "
"в отеле`, `Авиабилет`). Затем в поле :guilabel:`Категория` выберите "
"соответствующий вариант из выпадающего меню (например, :guilabel:`Питание`, "
":guilabel:`Мили`, :guilabel:`Поездки и проживание`)."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:194
msgid ""
"Expense categories can be added and modified by navigating "
"to :menuselection:`Expenses app --> Configuration --> Expense Categories`."
msgstr ""
"Категории расходов можно добавлять и изменять, перейдя в "
":menuselection:`Приложение Расходы --> Настройка --> Категории расходов`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:197
msgid ""
"Then, enter the total amount of the expense in the :guilabel:`Total` field, "
"as well as any :guilabel:`Included Taxes` that may apply. Next, ensure that "
"the correct :guilabel:`Employee` is selected, and designate who paid for the "
"expense in the :guilabel:`Paid By` field: the :guilabel:`Employee (to "
"reimburse)` or the :guilabel:`Company`."
msgstr ""
"Затем введите общую сумму расхода в поле :guilabel:`Total`, а также любые "
":guilabel:`Included Taxes`, которые могут применяться. Далее убедитесь, что "
"выбран правильный :guilabel:`Сотрудник`, и укажите, кто оплатил расход, в "
"поле :guilabel:`Paid By`: :guilabel:`Employee (to reimburse)` или "
":guilabel:`Company`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:202
msgid ""
"Next, in the :guilabel:`Customer to Reinvoice` field, select the appropriate "
"sales order from the drop-down menu. Then, select that same sales order "
"information from the :guilabel:`Analytic Distribution` field, as well."
msgstr ""
"Затем в поле :guilabel:`Customer to Reinvoice` выберите соответствующий "
"заказ на продажу из выпадающего меню. После этого выберите ту же информацию "
"о заказе на продажу в поле :guilabel:`Analytic Distribution`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:207
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Analytic Distribution` field will **only** have the "
"corresponding sales order as an option if the sales order contains a service "
"product that is billed based on *Timesheets*, *Milestones*, or *Delivered "
"Quantities*."
msgstr ""
"В поле :guilabel:`Analytic Distribution` соответствующий заказ на продажу "
"будет доступен в качестве опции **только** в том случае, если заказ на "
"продажу содержит сервисный продукт, который выставляется на основе "
"*Табелей*, *Этапов* или *Поставленного количества*."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:None
msgid ""
"How to properly fill out an expense form that's attached to a sales order in "
"Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Как правильно заполнить форму расхода, прикрепленную к заказу на продажу в "
"Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:215
msgid ""
"If there are any receipts that should be uploaded and attached to the "
"expense, click the :guilabel:`Attach Receipt` button, and upload the "
"necessary documents to the expense. This is **not** required, but it may "
"affect whether or not an expense is approved."
msgstr ""
"Если есть какие-либо чеки, которые следует загрузить и прикрепить к расходу, "
"нажмите кнопку :guilabel:`Attach Receipt` и загрузите необходимые документы "
"к расходу. Это **не** обязательно, но может повлиять на то, будет ли расход "
"утвержден."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:219
msgid ""
"When all the information has been entered, click :guilabel:`Create Report` "
"to create an expense report detailing all the expense information that was "
"just entered."
msgstr ""
"Когда вся информация введена, нажмите :guilabel:`Create Report`, чтобы "
"создать отчет о расходах с подробными сведениями обо всей введенной "
"информации о расходах."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:None
msgid "How an Expense Report Summary looks in Odoo Expenses."
msgstr "Как выглядит сводка отчета о расходах в Odoo Expenses."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:226
msgid ""
"Then, there's the option to :guilabel:`Submit to Manager` for approval. Once "
"approved, the :guilabel:`Report in Next Payslip` appears."
msgstr ""
"Затем появляется опция :guilabel:`Submit to Manager` для утверждения. После "
"утверждения отображается :guilabel:`Report in Next Payslip`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:229
msgid ""
"To showcase a complete flow in this example, select :guilabel:`Submit to "
"Manager`. Then, the manager would click :guilabel:`Approve` to approve this "
"expense, and click :guilabel:`Post Journal Entries` to post this expense to "
"the accounting journal."
msgstr ""
"Чтобы продемонстрировать полный процесс в этом примере, выберите "
":guilabel:`Submit to Manager`. Затем менеджер должен нажать "
":guilabel:`Approve`, чтобы утвердить этот расход, и нажать :guilabel:`Post "
"Journal Entries`, чтобы провести этот расход в бухгалтерском журнале."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:234
msgid "Invoice expenses"
msgstr "Выставление счетов за расходы"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:236
msgid ""
"To invoice a customer for an :ref:`expense on a sales order <sales/invoicing/"
"add-expenses-sales-order>`, navigate to the related sales order, either from "
"the :menuselection:`Sales` app or from the expense report in "
"the :menuselection:`Expenses` app. From the expense report, click "
"the :guilabel:`Sales Orders` smart button at the top of the page."
msgstr ""
"Чтобы выставить клиенту счет за :ref:`расход по заказу на продажу <sales/"
"invoicing/add-expenses-sales-order>`, перейдите к связанному заказу на "
"продажу либо из приложения :menuselection:`Продажи`, либо из отчета о "
"расходах в приложении :menuselection:`Расходы`. Из отчета о расходах нажмите "
"смарт-кнопку :guilabel:`Sales Orders` в верхней части страницы."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:241
msgid ""
"If the expense report was linked to the sales order, the newly-configured "
"expense now has its own line in the :guilabel:`Order Lines` tab, and can be "
"invoiced to the customer."
msgstr ""
"Если отчет о расходах был привязан к заказу на продажу, у только что "
"настроенного расхода теперь есть собственная строка на вкладке "
":guilabel:`Order Lines`, и он может быть выставлен клиенту в счет."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:None
msgid ""
"An expense appearing on Order Lines tab of a Sales Order in Odoo Sales "
"application."
msgstr ""
"Расход, отображаемый на вкладке Order Lines заказа на продажу в приложении "
"Odoo Sales."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:248
msgid ""
"To invoice the customer for the expense on the sales order, "
"click :guilabel:`Create Invoice`, select :guilabel:`Regular Invoice` from "
"the :guilabel:`Create invoices` pop-up window, then click :guilabel:`Create "
"Draft Invoice`."
msgstr ""
"Чтобы выставить клиенту счет за расход по заказу на продажу, нажмите "
":guilabel:`Create Invoice`, выберите :guilabel:`Regular Invoice` во "
"всплывающем окне :guilabel:`Create invoices`, затем нажмите "
":guilabel:`Create Draft Invoice`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:252
msgid ""
"Doing so reveals a :guilabel:`Customer Invoice Draft` for the expense. Then, "
"the invoicing process can be completed as usual."
msgstr ""
"При этом отобразится :guilabel:`Customer Invoice Draft` для расхода. Затем "
"процесс выставления счета можно завершить обычным образом."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:None
msgid ""
"Sample customer invoice for an expense generated from a sales order in Odoo "
"Sales."
msgstr ""
"Образец счета клиенту за расход, сформированный из заказа на продажу в Odoo "
"Sales."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:260
msgid "Purchase configuration"
msgstr "Настройка закупок"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:262
msgid ""
"In order to invoice a customer for purchases made on a sales order, the "
"*Purchase* application **must** be installed."
msgstr ""
"Чтобы выставить клиенту счет за закупки, сделанные по заказу на продажу, "
"приложение *Закупка* **должно** быть установлено."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:265
msgid ""
"To install the *Purchase* application, navigate to :menuselection:`Odoo main "
"dashboard --> Apps`. Then, on the :guilabel:`Apps` page, locate "
"the :guilabel:`Purchase` app block, and click :guilabel:`Activate`. The page "
"automatically refreshes and returns to the main Odoo dashboard, where "
"the :guilabel:`Purchase` app is now available to access."
msgstr ""
"Чтобы установить приложение *Закупка*, перейдите в :menuselection:`Главная "
"панель Odoo --> Apps`. Затем на странице :guilabel:`Apps` найдите блок "
"приложения :guilabel:`Закупка` и нажмите :guilabel:`Activate`. Страница "
"автоматически обновится и вернется к главной панели Odoo, где приложение "
":guilabel:`Закупка` теперь доступно."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:273
msgid "Add purchase to sales order"
msgstr "Добавление закупки к заказу на продажу"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:275
msgid ""
"To add a purchase to a sales order, a purchase order must first be created. "
"To create a purchase order, navigate to :menuselection:`Purchase app --> "
"New` to reveal a blank purchase order form."
msgstr ""
"Чтобы добавить закупку к заказу на продажу, сначала необходимо создать заказ "
"на закупку. Для создания заказа на закупку перейдите в "
":menuselection:`Закупка --> Создать`, чтобы открыть пустую форму заказа на "
"закупку."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:278
msgid ""
"First, add a :guilabel:`Vendor` to the purchase order. Then, under "
"the :guilabel:`Products` tab, click the :guilabel:`extra column options` "
"drop-down menu, represented by two horizontal lines with dots on them, "
"located to the far-right of the column headers. From that drop-down menu, "
"select :guilabel:`Analytic Distribution`."
msgstr ""
"Сначала добавьте :guilabel:`Поставщика` в заказ на закупку. Затем на вкладке "
":guilabel:`Товары` нажмите на выпадающее меню :guilabel:`дополнительных "
"параметров столбцов`, представленное двумя горизонтальными линиями с "
"точками, расположенное в крайнем правом углу заголовков столбцов. В этом "
"выпадающем меню выберите :guilabel:`Аналитическое распределение`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:None
msgid ""
"How to add analytic distribution column on purchase order form in Odoo "
"Purchase."
msgstr ""
"Как добавить столбец аналитического распределения в форме заказа на закупку "
"в Odoo Закупка."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:287
msgid ""
"After adding the :guilabel:`Analytic Distribution` column to the headers on "
"the :guilabel:`Products` tab of the purchase order form, proceed to add the "
"product(s) to the purchase order. To do that, click :guilabel:`Add a "
"product`, and select the desired product from the drop-down menu. Repeat for "
"all the products to add."
msgstr ""
"После добавления столбца :guilabel:`Аналитическое распределение` к "
"заголовкам на вкладке :guilabel:`Товары` формы заказа на закупку, добавьте "
"товар(ы) в заказ на закупку. Для этого нажмите :guilabel:`Добавить товар` и "
"выберите нужный товар из выпадающего меню. Повторите для всех добавляемых "
"товаров."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:293
msgid ""
"In order for a purchase to be properly invoiced on a sales order, the "
"product on the purchase order **must** be marked as :guilabel:`Can be "
"Expensed`, have an :guilabel:`Invoicing Policy` set to :guilabel:`Delivered "
"quantities`, and have the :guilabel:`At cost` option selected in "
"the :guilabel:`Re-Invoice Expenses` field on its product form."
msgstr ""
"Для того чтобы закупка была правильно выставлена в счёте к заказу на "
"продажу, товар в заказе на закупку **должен** быть отмечен как "
":guilabel:`Может быть списан как расход`, иметь :guilabel:`Политику "
"выставления счетов`, установленную как :guilabel:`Доставленное количество`, "
"и иметь выбранный параметр :guilabel:`По себестоимости` в поле "
":guilabel:`Перевыставление расходов` на форме товара."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:0
msgid ""
"Product settings for a purchase order to be invoiced on a sales order in "
"Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Настройки товара для выставления заказа на закупку в счёте к заказу на "
"продажу в Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:302
msgid ""
"Then, select the appropriate :guilabel:`Analytic Distribution` associated "
"with the sales order to which this purchase order is related. To do that, "
"click the empty :guilabel:`Analytic Distribution` field to reveal "
"an :guilabel:`Analytic` pop-up window."
msgstr ""
"Затем выберите соответствующее :guilabel:`Аналитическое распределение`, "
"связанное с заказом на продажу, к которому относится данный заказ на "
"закупку. Для этого нажмите на пустое поле :guilabel:`Аналитическое "
"распределение`, чтобы открыть всплывающее окно :guilabel:`Аналитика`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:306
msgid ""
"Then, from the :guilabel:`Departments` drop-down menu, select the analytic "
"distribution associated with the desired sales order to be invoiced for the "
"purchase."
msgstr ""
"Затем в выпадающем меню :guilabel:`Отделы` выберите аналитическое "
"распределение, связанное с нужным заказом на продажу, по которому будет "
"выставлен счёт за закупку."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:None
msgid ""
"How to select the Analytic Distribution department from a purchase order in "
"Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Как выбрать отдел аналитического распределения из заказа на закупку в Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:313
msgid ""
"Once all the information is entered in the :guilabel:`Products` tab of the "
"purchase order, confirm the order by clicking :guilabel:`Confirm Order`. "
"Then, click :guilabel:`Receive Products` when the products have been "
"received. This creates a receipt form."
msgstr ""
"После ввода всей информации на вкладке :guilabel:`Товары` заказа на закупку "
"подтвердите заказ, нажав :guilabel:`Подтвердить заказ`. Затем нажмите "
":guilabel:`Получить товары`, когда товары будут получены. Это создаст форму "
"получения."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:318
msgid ""
"If any serial/lot numbers must be entered before validating the receipt of "
"products, then on the receipt form, click the :guilabel:`details` icon "
"represented by four horizontal lines located to the far-right of the product "
"line."
msgstr ""
"Если перед подтверждением получения товаров необходимо ввести серийные "
"номера/номера партий, то на форме получения нажмите значок "
":guilabel:`подробности`, представленный четырьмя горизонтальными линиями, "
"расположенный в крайнем правом углу строки товара."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:322
msgid ""
"This reveals a :guilabel:`Detailed Operations` tab, in which the "
"necessary :guilabel:`Lot/Serial Number(s)` and :guilabel:`Done` quantity can "
"be added. When ready, click :guilabel:`Confirm` to confirm the data."
msgstr ""
"Откроется вкладка :guilabel:`Подробные операции`, в которой можно добавить "
"необходимые :guilabel:`Номер партии/серийный номер` и количество "
":guilabel:`Выполнено`. Когда всё готово, нажмите :guilabel:`Подтвердить`, "
"чтобы подтвердить данные."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:326
msgid "Then, click :guilabel:`Validate` to validate the purchase order."
msgstr "Затем нажмите :guilabel:`Проверить`, чтобы проверить заказ на закупку."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:328
msgid ""
"Next, return to the purchase order, via the breadcrumb links at the top of "
"the page, and click :guilabel:`Create Bill` to create a vendor bill that can "
"be invoiced to the customer on the attached sales order."
msgstr ""
"Далее вернитесь к заказу на закупку с помощью навигационных ссылок в верхней "
"части страницы и нажмите :guilabel:`Создать счёт`, чтобы создать счёт "
"поставщика, который можно выставить клиенту по прикреплённому заказу на "
"продажу."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:None
msgid ""
"Vendor bill draft for a purchase order to be invoiced to a customer in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Черновик счёта поставщика для заказа на закупку, который будет выставлен "
"клиенту в Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:337
msgid ""
"Make sure to enter a :guilabel:`Bill Date` on the :guilabel:`Vendor Bill "
"Draft` before confirming. If a :guilabel:`Bill Date` is *not* entered, an "
"error window appears, requesting that information to be entered before "
"confirmation can occur."
msgstr ""
"Обязательно укажите :guilabel:`Дату счёта` в :guilabel:`Черновике счёта "
"поставщика` перед подтверждением. Если :guilabel:`Дата счёта` *не* указана, "
"появится окно с ошибкой, требующее ввести эту информацию перед "
"подтверждением."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:341
msgid ""
"Then, click :guilabel:`Confirm` to confirm the vendor bill, which is then "
"automatically added to the sales order, where it can be invoiced directly to "
"the customer attached to it."
msgstr ""
"Затем нажмите :guilabel:`Подтвердить`, чтобы подтвердить счёт поставщика, "
"который затем автоматически добавится к заказу на продажу, где его можно "
"будет выставить непосредственно прикреплённому к нему клиенту."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:345
msgid "Invoice purchase"
msgstr "Выставление счёта за закупку"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:347
msgid ""
"To invoice a customer for a purchase on a sales order, first :ref:`add the "
"purchase to the sales order <sales/invoicing/add-purchase-to-sales-order>`, "
"then navigate to the desired sales order in the :menuselection:`Sales` app."
msgstr ""
"Чтобы выставить клиенту счёт за закупку по заказу на продажу, сначала "
":ref:`добавьте закупку к заказу на продажу <sales/invoicing/add-purchase-to-"
"sales-order>`, затем перейдите к нужному заказу на продажу в приложении "
":menuselection:`Продажи`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:351
msgid ""
"On the sales order that was attached to the purchase order, the purchased "
"product now has its own product line under the :guilabel:`Order Lines` tab, "
"and it is ready to be invoiced."
msgstr ""
"В заказе на продажу, который был прикреплён к заказу на закупку, "
"приобретённый товар теперь имеет собственную строку товара на вкладке "
":guilabel:`Строки заказа`, и он готов к выставлению счёта."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:None
msgid ""
"Purchase order product on sales order to be invoiced to customer via Odoo "
"Sales."
msgstr ""
"Заказ продукта на закупку по заказу на продажу для выставления счета клиенту "
"через Odoo Продажи."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:358
msgid ""
"To invoice the customer for the purchase, simply click :guilabel:`Create "
"Invoice`, select :guilabel:`Regular Invoice` from the :guilabel:`Create "
"invoices` pop-up window, then click :guilabel:`Create Draft Invoice`."
msgstr ""
"Чтобы выставить счет клиенту за закупку, просто нажмите :guilabel:`Создать "
"счет`, выберите :guilabel:`Обычный счет` во всплывающем окне "
":guilabel:`Создать счета`, затем нажмите :guilabel:`Создать черновик счета`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:362
msgid ""
"Doing so reveals a :guilabel:`Customer Invoice Draft` with the newly-added "
"purchase order product in the :guilabel:`Invoice Lines` tab."
msgstr ""
"При этом откроется :guilabel:`Черновик счета клиента` с только что "
"добавленным продуктом заказа на закупку на вкладке :guilabel:`Строки счета`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:None
msgid ""
"Customer invoice draft with purchase product attached to sales order in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Черновик счета клиента с продуктом закупки, прикрепленным к заказу на "
"продажу в Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:369
msgid ""
"To complete the invoicing process, click :guilabel:`Confirm` to confirm the "
"invoice, and then click :guilabel:`Register Payment` in "
"the :guilabel:`Register Payment` pop-up form."
msgstr ""
"Чтобы завершить процесс выставления счета, нажмите :guilabel:`Подтвердить` "
"для подтверждения счета, а затем нажмите :guilabel:`Зарегистрировать платеж` "
"во всплывающей форме :guilabel:`Регистрация платежа`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices.rst:5
msgid "Products & Prices"
msgstr "Товары и цены"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:3
msgid "Use eWallets and gift cards"
msgstr "Использование электронных кошельков и подарочных карт"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:5
msgid ""
"With Odoo, customers can use **eWallets** and **gift cards** for online and "
"in-store shopping."
msgstr ""
"В Odoo клиенты могут использовать **электронные кошельки** и **подарочные "
"карты** для покупок онлайн и в магазине."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:7
msgid ""
"To enable eWallets and gift cards for eCommerce and Point of Sale (PoS), "
"first enable :guilabel:`Discounts, Loyalty & Gift Card` "
"under :menuselection:`Sales app --> Configuration --> Settings --> Pricing "
"section`. Once enabled, go to :menuselection:`Sales app --> Products --> "
"Gift cards & eWallet` and :guilabel:`Create` a new eWallet or gift card "
"program."
msgstr ""
"Чтобы включить электронные кошельки и подарочные карты для электронной "
"коммерции и POS, сначала включите :guilabel:`Скидки, лояльность и подарочные "
"карты` в разделе :menuselection:`Приложение Продажи --> Конфигурация --> "
"Настройки --> раздел Ценообразование`. После включения перейдите в "
":menuselection:`Приложение Продажи --> Продукты --> Подарочные карты и "
"электронный кошелек` и :guilabel:`Создайте` новую программу электронного "
"кошелька или подарочной карты."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:13
msgid "eWallets"
msgstr "Электронный кошелек"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:15
msgid ""
"eWallets allow customers to save credits on their online account and use "
"these credits as a payment method when buying items in an online store or a "
"brick-and-mortar store. eWallets can also be used to centralize "
"multiple :ref:`gift cards <ewallet_gift/gift-cards>`."
msgstr ""
"Электронные кошельки позволяют клиентам сохранять кредиты в своей онлайн-"
"учетной записи и использовать эти кредиты в качестве способа оплаты при "
"покупке товаров в интернет-магазине или обычном магазине. Электронные "
"кошельки также можно использовать для централизации нескольких "
":ref:`подарочных карт <ewallet_gift/gift-cards>`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:19
msgid ""
"Before creating an eWallet program, it is necessary to create an eWallet "
"**top-up** product. Top-ups are pre-defined digital credit values added to "
"an eWallet in exchange for its equivalent in real currency. These credits "
"can then be used as a payment method in the eCommerce shop or :abbr:`PoS "
"(Point of Sale)`. Top-up values can be of different amounts."
msgstr ""
"Перед созданием программы электронного кошелька необходимо создать продукт "
"**пополнения** электронного кошелька. Пополнения — это предопределенные "
"значения цифрового кредита, добавляемые в электронный кошелек в обмен на их "
"эквивалент в реальной валюте. Эти кредиты затем могут использоваться в "
"качестве способа оплаты в интернет-магазине или :abbr:`POS (точка продаж)`. "
"Значения пополнения могут быть различных сумм."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:25
msgid ""
"A $50 top-up can be bought for $50, and adds that same amount of credits to "
"the eWallet."
msgstr ""
"Пополнение на $50 можно купить за $50, и оно добавляет такую же сумму "
"кредитов в электронный кошелек."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:27
msgid ""
"To create a top-up product, go to :menuselection:`Sales app --> Products --> "
"Products` and :guilabel:`Create` a new product. On the product template, "
"configure the options as follows:"
msgstr ""
"Чтобы создать продукт пополнения, перейдите в :menuselection:`Приложение "
"Продажи --> Продукты --> Продукты` и :guilabel:`Создайте` новый продукт. В "
"шаблоне продукта настройте параметры следующим образом:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:30
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Product Name`: enter a name for the top-up product (for example, "
"`$50 Top-Up`)"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Название продукта`: введите название продукта пополнения "
"(например, `Пополнение на $50`)"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:31
#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:92
msgid ":guilabel:`Can be Sold`: enabled"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Может быть продано`: включено"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:32
#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:93
msgid ":guilabel:`Product Type`: select :guilabel:`Service`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Тип продукта`: выберите :guilabel:`Услуга`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:33
#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:94
msgid ":guilabel:`Invoicing Policy`: select :guilabel:`Prepaid/Fixed Price`"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Политика выставления счетов`: выберите :guilabel:`Предоплата/"
"Фиксированная цена`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:34
#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:95
msgid ":guilabel:`Create on Order`: select :guilabel:`Nothing`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Создать при заказе`: выберите :guilabel:`Ничего`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:35
msgid ":guilabel:`Sales Price`: enter the amount of the top-up"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Цена продажи`: введите сумму пополнения"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:38
msgid ""
"In order to have eWallet top-ups of different amounts, create multiple top-"
"up products and modify the :guilabel:`Sales Price` accordingly."
msgstr ""
"Чтобы иметь пополнения электронного кошелька разных сумм, создайте несколько "
"продуктов пополнения и измените :guilabel:`Цену продажи` соответствующим "
"образом."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:41
msgid ""
"Once the top-up is created, go to :menuselection:`Sales app --> Products --> "
"Gift cards & eWallet` to :guilabel:`Create` an eWallet program. The "
"following configuration options are available:"
msgstr ""
"После создания пополнения перейдите в :menuselection:`Приложение Продажи --> "
"Продукты --> Подарочные карты и электронный кошелек`, чтобы "
":guilabel:`Создать` программу электронного кошелька. Доступны следующие "
"параметры конфигурации:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:44
msgid ":guilabel:`Program Name`: enter a name for the eWallet program"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Название программы`: введите название программы электронного "
"кошелька"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:45
msgid ":guilabel:`Program Type`: select :guilabel:`eWallet`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Тип программы`: выберите :guilabel:`Электронный кошелек`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:46
msgid ""
":guilabel:`eWallet Products`: select the eWallet top-up created earlier. "
"Repeat the process if you created top-ups of different amounts."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Продукты электронного кошелька`: выберите созданное ранее "
"пополнение электронного кошелька. Повторите процесс, если вы создали "
"пополнения на разные суммы."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:48
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Email template`: select the email template used for the email "
"sent to the customer. To create a new template, click on the field, "
"select :guilabel:`Search More`, and then click :guilabel:`Create`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Шаблон электронного письма`: выберите шаблон электронного письма, "
"используемый для письма, отправляемого клиенту. Чтобы создать новый шаблон, "
"нажмите на поле, выберите :guilabel:`Расширенный поиск`, а затем нажмите "
":guilabel:`Создать`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:51
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Currency`: select the currency to use for the eWallet program"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Валюта`: выберите валюту для использования в программе "
"электронного кошелька"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:52
#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:115
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Company`: select the company for which the program is valid and "
"available"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Компания`: выберите компанию, для которой программа действительна "
"и доступна"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:53
#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:116
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Available On`: select the applications on which the program is "
"valid and available"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Доступно в`: выберите приложения, в которых программа "
"действительна и доступна"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:54
#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:117
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Website`: select the website on which the program is valid and "
"available. Leave this field empty to include all websites."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Веб-сайт`: выберите веб-сайт, на котором программа действительна "
"и доступна. Оставьте это поле пустым, чтобы включить все веб-сайты."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:56
#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:119
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Point of Sale`: select the :abbr:`PoS (Point of Sale)` in which "
"the program is valid and available. Leave this field empty to include "
"all :abbr:`PoS (Point of Sale)`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Точка продаж`: выберите :abbr:`POS (точка продаж)`, в которой "
"программа действительна и доступна. Оставьте это поле пустым, чтобы включить "
"все :abbr:`POS (точки продаж)`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:None
msgid "eWallet program configuration page"
msgstr "Страница настройки программы электронного кошелька"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:63
msgid ""
"Once the program is configured, click the :guilabel:`Generate eWallet` "
"button in the upper-left corner to generate eWallets. eWallets can be "
"generated based on :guilabel:`Customers` and/or :guilabel:`Customer Tags`. "
"The quantity is automatically adapted according to the :guilabel:`Customers` "
"and :guilabel:`Customer Tags` selected. Then, set the :guilabel:`eWallet "
"value`. Finally, set the :guilabel:`Valid Until` period if applicable."
msgstr ""
"После настройки программы нажмите кнопку :guilabel:`Создать электронный "
"кошелек` в левом верхнем углу для создания электронных кошельков. "
"Электронные кошельки могут создаваться на основе :guilabel:`Клиентов` и/или "
":guilabel:`Тегов клиентов`. Количество автоматически адаптируется в "
"соответствии с выбранными :guilabel:`Клиентами` и :guilabel:`Тегами "
"клиентов`. Затем установите :guilabel:`Стоимость электронного кошелька`. "
"Наконец, при необходимости установите период :guilabel:`Действителен до`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:69
msgid ""
"Generated eWallets can be accessed through the :guilabel:`eWallets` smart "
"button in the upper-right corner. From there, :guilabel:`Send` "
"or :guilabel:`Share` the eWallets via email or a URL link."
msgstr ""
"Доступ к созданным электронным кошелькам можно получить через смарт-кнопку "
":guilabel:`Электронные кошельки` в правом верхнем углу. Оттуда можно "
":guilabel:`Отправить` или :guilabel:`Поделиться` электронными кошельками по "
"электронной почте или через URL-ссылку."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:None
msgid "eWallets send and share buttons"
msgstr "Кнопки отправки и общего доступа для электронных кошельков"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:76
msgid ""
"Click on an eWallet to change the :guilabel:`Expiration "
"Date`, :guilabel:`Partner`, or :guilabel:`Balance`. The :guilabel:`Code` of "
"an eWallet *cannot* be changed, deleted, or duplicated."
msgstr ""
"Нажмите на электронный кошелек, чтобы изменить :guilabel:`Дату истечения "
"срока действия`, :guilabel:`Контрагента` или :guilabel:`Баланс`. "
":guilabel:`Код` электронного кошелька *нельзя* изменить, удалить или "
"дублировать."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:82
msgid "Gift cards"
msgstr "Подарочные сертификаты"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:84
msgid ""
"Gift cards can be purchased by customers, and in turn used as a payment "
"method upon checkout at an eCommerce shop or :abbr:`PoS (Point of Sale)`."
msgstr ""
"Подарочные карты могут быть приобретены клиентами и, в свою очередь, "
"использованы в качестве способа оплаты при оформлении заказа в интернет-"
"магазине электронной коммерции или :abbr:`POS (точке продаж)`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:87
msgid ""
"Before creating a new gift card program, it is necessary to first create "
"gift cards as products. To do so, go to :menuselection:`Sales app --> "
"Products --> Products` and :guilabel:`Create` a product. On the product "
"template, configure the options as follows:"
msgstr ""
"Перед созданием новой программы подарочных карт необходимо сначала создать "
"подарочные карты как продукты. Для этого перейдите в "
":menuselection:`Приложение Продажи --> Продукты --> Продукты` и "
":guilabel:`Создайте` продукт. В шаблоне продукта настройте параметры "
"следующим образом:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:91
msgid ":guilabel:`Product Name`: enter a name for the gift card product"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Название продукта`: введите название продукта подарочной карты"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:96
msgid ":guilabel:`Sales Price`: enter the amount of the gift card"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Цена продажи`: введите сумму подарочной карты"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:99
msgid ""
"In order to have gift cards of different amounts, create multiple gift card "
"products and modify the :guilabel:`Sales Price` accordingly."
msgstr ""
"Чтобы иметь подарочные карты разных номиналов, создайте несколько продуктов "
"подарочных карт и соответствующим образом измените :guilabel:`Цену продажи`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:102
msgid ""
"Once the gift card product is created, go to :menuselection:`Sales app --> "
"Products --> Gift cards & eWallet` to :guilabel:`Create` a gift card "
"program. The following configuration options are available:"
msgstr ""
"После создания продукта подарочной карты перейдите в "
":menuselection:`Приложение Продажи --> Продукты --> Подарочные карты и "
"электронные кошельки`, чтобы :guilabel:`Создать` программу подарочных карт. "
"Доступны следующие параметры настройки:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:106
msgid ":guilabel:`Program Name`: enter a name for the gift card program"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Название программы`: введите название программы подарочных карт"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:107
msgid ":guilabel:`Program Type`: select :guilabel:`Gift Card`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Тип программы`: выберите :guilabel:`Подарочная карта`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:108
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Gift Card Products`: select the gift card product created "
"earlier. Repeat the process if you created gift card products of different "
"amounts."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Продукты подарочных карт`: выберите созданный ранее продукт "
"подарочной карты. Повторите процесс, если вы создали продукты подарочных "
"карт разных номиналов."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:110
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Email template`: select the default :guilabel:`Gift Card: Gift "
"Card Information` template, or create a new template by clicking on the "
"field, selecting :guilabel:`Search More`, and then "
"clicking :guilabel:`Create`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Шаблон электронного письма`: выберите стандартный шаблон "
":guilabel:`Gift Card: Gift Card Information` или создайте новый шаблон, "
"нажав на поле, выбрав :guilabel:`Искать ещё`, а затем нажав "
":guilabel:`Создать`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:113
msgid ":guilabel:`Print Report`: select :guilabel:`Gift Card`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Печать отчёта`: выберите :guilabel:`Подарочная карта`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:114
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Currency`: select the currency to use for the gift card program"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Валюта`: выберите валюту для программы подарочных карт"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:None
msgid "Gift card program configuration page"
msgstr "Страница настройки программы подарочных карт"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:126
msgid ""
"Once the program is configured, click the :guilabel:`Generate Gift Cards` "
"button in the upper-left corner to generate gift cards. Gift cards can be "
"generated either for :guilabel:`Anonymous Customers` or :guilabel:`Selected "
"Customers`. Set the :guilabel:`Quantity to generate` "
"for :guilabel:`Anonymous Customers`, or select the :guilabel:`Customers` and/"
"or :guilabel:`Customer Tags` for :guilabel:`Selected Customers`. Then, set "
"the :guilabel:`Gift Card value`. Finally, set the :guilabel:`Valid Until` "
"period if applicable."
msgstr ""
"После настройки программы нажмите кнопку :guilabel:`Сгенерировать подарочные "
"карты` в левом верхнем углу, чтобы сгенерировать подарочные карты. "
"Подарочные карты могут быть сгенерированы либо для :guilabel:`анонимных "
"клиентов`, либо для :guilabel:`выбранных клиентов`. Установите "
":guilabel:`Количество для генерации` для :guilabel:`анонимных клиентов` или "
"выберите :guilabel:`Клиентов` и/или :guilabel:`Теги клиентов` для "
":guilabel:`выбранных клиентов`. Затем установите :guilabel:`Номинал "
"подарочной карты`. Наконец, установите период :guilabel:`Действительна до`, "
"если применимо."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:133
msgid ""
"Generated gift cards can be accessed through the :guilabel:`Gift Cards` "
"smart button in the upper-right corner. From there, :guilabel:`Send` "
"or :guilabel:`Share` the gift cards via email or a URL link."
msgstr ""
"Доступ к сгенерированным подарочным картам можно получить с помощью кнопки "
":guilabel:`Подарочные карты` в правом верхнем углу. Оттуда можно "
":guilabel:`Отправить` или :guilabel:`Поделиться` подарочными картами по "
"электронной почте или через URL-ссылку."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:None
msgid "Gift cards send and share buttons"
msgstr "Кнопки отправки и публикации подарочных карт"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:141
msgid ""
"Click on a gift card to change the :guilabel:`Expiration "
"Date`, :guilabel:`Partner`, or :guilabel:`Balance`. The :guilabel:`Code` of "
"a gift card *cannot* be changed, deleted, or duplicated."
msgstr ""
"Нажмите на подарочную карту, чтобы изменить :guilabel:`Дату истечения`, "
":guilabel:`Контрагента` или :guilabel:`Баланс`. :guilabel:`Код` подарочной "
"карты *нельзя* изменить, удалить или дублировать."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/loyalty_discount.rst:3
msgid "Discount and loyalty programs"
msgstr "Программы скидок и лояльности"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/loyalty_discount.rst:5
msgid ""
"The Odoo *Sales*, *eCommerce*, and *Point of Sale* applications allow users "
"to create discount and loyalty programs that customers can use for online "
"and in-store shopping. These programs offer more varied, public, and time-"
"sensitive pricing options than :doc:`pricelists </applications/sales/sales/"
"products_prices/prices/pricing>`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/loyalty_discount.rst:11
msgid "Configure the settings"
msgstr "Настроить параметры"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/loyalty_discount.rst:13
msgid ""
"To begin using discount and loyalty programs, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Sales --> Configuration --> Settings`. Under "
"the :guilabel:`Pricing` heading, activate the :guilabel:`Discounts, Loyalty "
"& Gift Card` setting by checking the box next to the feature. Finally, "
"click :guilabel:`Save` to save the changes."
msgstr ""
"Чтобы начать использовать программы скидок и лояльности, перейдите в "
":menuselection:`Продажи --> Конфигурация --> Настройки`. В разделе "
":guilabel:`Ценообразование` активируйте настройку :guilabel:`Скидки, "
"лояльность и подарочные карты`, установив флажок рядом с функцией. Наконец, "
"нажмите :guilabel:`Сохранить`, чтобы сохранить изменения."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/loyalty_discount.rst:19
msgid "Configure discount and loyalty programs"
msgstr "Настройка программ скидок и лояльности"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/loyalty_discount.rst:21
msgid ""
"To create discount and loyalty programs, go to :menuselection:`Sales --> "
"Products --> Discount & Loyalty`."
msgstr ""
"Чтобы создать программы скидок и лояльности, перейдите в "
":menuselection:`Продажи --> Продукты --> Скидки и лояльность`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/loyalty_discount.rst:24
msgid ""
"If no discount or loyalty programs have been created yet, Odoo provides a "
"choice of templates to help create the first program. Choose one of the "
"template cards, or click :guilabel:`New` to create a new program from "
"scratch."
msgstr ""
"Если программы скидок или лояльности ещё не были созданы, Odoo предлагает "
"набор шаблонов для создания первой программы. Выберите одну из карточек "
"шаблонов или нажмите :guilabel:`Создать`, чтобы создать новую программу с "
"нуля."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/loyalty_discount.rst:28
msgid ""
"Or, if there are already existing programs, select an existing program to "
"edit it."
msgstr ""
"Или, если уже есть существующие программы, выберите существующую программу "
"для её редактирования."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/loyalty_discount.rst:None
msgid "Discount and loyalty program template cards."
msgstr "Карточки шаблонов программ скидок и лояльности."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/loyalty_discount.rst:35
msgid ""
"Templates **only** appear when no programs have been created, and they "
"disappear once the first program is created."
msgstr ""
"Шаблоны появляются **только** тогда, когда не создано ни одной программы, и "
"исчезают после создания первой программы."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/loyalty_discount.rst:38
msgid "Creating or editing a program opens the program form."
msgstr "Создание или редактирование программы открывает форму программы."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/loyalty_discount.rst:None
msgid "Program options on the loyalty program form."
msgstr "Параметры программы на форме программы лояльности."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/loyalty_discount.rst:44
msgid "The program form contains the following fields:"
msgstr "Форма программы содержит следующие поля:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/loyalty_discount.rst:46
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Program Name`: Enter the name of the program in this field. The "
"program name is **not** visible to the customer."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Название программы`: Введите название программы в это поле. "
"Название программы **не** отображается клиенту."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/loyalty_discount.rst:48
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Program Type`: Select the desired :ref:`program type <sales/"
"pricing_management/program-types>` from the drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Тип программы`: Выберите нужный :ref:`тип программы <sales/"
"pricing_management/program-types>` из выпадающего меню."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/loyalty_discount.rst:50
msgid ":guilabel:`Currency`: Select the currency used for the program."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Валюта`: Выберите валюту, используемую для программы."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/loyalty_discount.rst:51
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Pricelist`: If desired, select a pricelist from the drop-down "
"menu to have this loyalty program applied to a specific pricelist (and "
"customers attached to the pricelist). More than one pricelist can be "
"selected in this field. When a single loyalty program is linked to several "
"pricelists, it makes it viable for different customer segments to have "
"different pricelists, but the *same* loyalty programs. If this field is left "
"blank, the program applies to everyone, regardless of pricelist."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Прайс-лист`: При необходимости выберите прайс-лист из выпадающего "
"меню, чтобы применить эту программу лояльности к определенному прайс-листу "
"(и клиентам, привязанным к прайс-листу). В этом поле можно выбрать несколько "
"прайс-листов. Когда одна программа лояльности привязана к нескольким прайс-"
"листам, это позволяет разным сегментам клиентов иметь разные прайс-листы, но "
"*одинаковые* программы лояльности. Если это поле оставить пустым, программа "
"применяется ко всем, независимо от прайс-листа."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/loyalty_discount.rst:57
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Points Unit`: Enter the name of the points used for "
"the :guilabel:`Loyalty Cards` program (e.g. `Loyalty Points`). The points "
"unit name *is* visible to the customer. This field is **only** available "
"when the :guilabel:`Program Type` is set to :guilabel:`Loyalty Cards`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Единица баллов`: Введите название баллов, используемых для "
"программы :guilabel:`Карты лояльности` (например, `Баллы лояльности`). "
"Название единицы баллов *отображается* клиенту. Это поле доступно **только** "
"когда :guilabel:`Тип программы` установлен на :guilabel:`Карты лояльности`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/loyalty_discount.rst:60
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Start Date`: Select the date on which the program becomes valid. "
"Leave this field blank if the program should always be valid and not expire."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Дата начала`: Выберите дату, с которой программа становится "
"действительной. Оставьте это поле пустым, если программа должна быть всегда "
"действительной и не истекать."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/loyalty_discount.rst:62
msgid ""
":guilabel:`End Date`: Select the date on which the program stops being "
"valid. Leave this field blank if the program should always be valid and not "
"expire."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Дата окончания`: Выберите дату, с которой программа перестает "
"быть действительной. Оставьте это поле пустым, если программа должна быть "
"всегда действительной и не истекать."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/loyalty_discount.rst:64
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Limit Usage`: If desired, tick this checkbox, and enter a number "
"of :guilabel:`usages` to limit the number of times the program can be used "
"during the validity period."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Ограничить использование`: При необходимости установите этот "
"флажок и введите количество :guilabel:`использований`, чтобы ограничить "
"количество раз, которое программа может быть использована в течение периода "
"действия."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/loyalty_discount.rst:66
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Company`: If working in a multi-company database, choose the one "
"company for which the program is available. If left blank, the program is "
"available to all companies in the database."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Компания`: Если работаете в многокомпанейной базе данных, "
"выберите одну компанию, для которой доступна программа. Если оставить "
"пустым, программа доступна для всех компаний в базе данных."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/loyalty_discount.rst:68
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Available On`: Select the apps on which the program is available."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Доступно в`: Выберите приложения, в которых доступна программа."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/loyalty_discount.rst:69
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Website`: Select a website on which the program is available. "
"Leave this field blank to make it available on all websites."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Веб-сайт`: Выберите веб-сайт, на котором доступна программа. "
"Оставьте это поле пустым, чтобы сделать её доступной на всех веб-сайтах."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/loyalty_discount.rst:71
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Point of Sale`: Select the point(s) of sale at which the program "
"is available. Leave this field blank to make it available at all :abbr:`PoS "
"(Point of Sale)`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Точка продажи`: Выберите точку (точки) продажи, в которых "
"доступна программа. Оставьте это поле пустым, чтобы сделать её доступной во "
"всех :abbr:`POS (торговых точках)`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/loyalty_discount.rst:75
msgid ""
"The options available on the program form vary depending on "
"the :ref:`Program Type <sales/pricing_management/program-types>` selected."
msgstr ""
"Доступные параметры на форме программы зависят от выбранного :ref:`типа "
"программы <sales/pricing_management/program-types>`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/loyalty_discount.rst:78
msgid ""
"All of the existing cards, codes, coupons, etc. that have been generated for "
"the program are accessible through the smart button located at the top of "
"the form."
msgstr ""
"Все существующие карты, коды, купоны и т. д., которые были созданы для "
"программы, доступны через умную кнопку, расположенную в верхней части формы."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/loyalty_discount.rst:None
msgid "Program items smart button on the loyalty program form."
msgstr "Умная кнопка элементов программы на форме программы лояльности."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/loyalty_discount.rst:86
msgid ""
"In Odoo 17 (and later), when a loyalty card or coupon is associated with a "
"contact in the database, a :guilabel:`Loyalty Cards` smart button "
"conditionally appears on the contact form."
msgstr ""
"В Odoo 17 (и более поздних версиях), когда карта лояльности или купон "
"связаны с контактом в базе данных, на форме контакта условно появляется "
"умная кнопка :guilabel:`Карты лояльности`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/loyalty_discount.rst:None
msgid ""
"The Loyalty Card smart button as it appears on a contact form in Odoo 17."
msgstr ""
"Умная кнопка карты лояльности в том виде, в котором она отображается на "
"форме контакта в Odoo 17."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/loyalty_discount.rst:93
msgid ""
"This smart button **only** appears if a loyalty card or coupon is associated "
"with the contact."
msgstr ""
"Эта умная кнопка появляется **только** в том случае, если с контактом "
"связана карта лояльности или купон."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/loyalty_discount.rst:98
msgid "Program types"
msgstr "Типы программ"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/loyalty_discount.rst:100
msgid ""
"The different :guilabel:`Program Types` available on the program form are:"
msgstr "На форме программы доступны следующие :guilabel:`Типы программ`:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/loyalty_discount.rst:102
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Coupons`: Generate and share single-use coupon codes that grant "
"immediate access to rewards."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Купоны`: генерируйте и делитесь кодами купонов для одноразового "
"использования, которые предоставляют немедленный доступ к вознаграждениям."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/loyalty_discount.rst:104
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Loyalty Cards`: When making purchases, the customer accumulates "
"points to exchange for rewards on current and/or future orders."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Карты лояльности`: при совершении покупок клиент накапливает "
"баллы для обмена на вознаграждения в текущих и/или будущих заказах."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/loyalty_discount.rst:106
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Promotions`: Set conditional rules for ordering products, which, "
"when fulfilled, grant access to rewards for the customer."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Акции`: установите условные правила для заказа товаров, которые "
"при выполнении предоставляют клиенту доступ к вознаграждениям."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/loyalty_discount.rst:108
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Discount Code`: Set codes which, when entered upon checkout, "
"grant discounts to the customer."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Код скидки`: установите коды, которые при вводе при оформлении "
"заказа предоставляют скидки клиенту."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/loyalty_discount.rst:110
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Buy X Get Y`: for every (X) item bought, the customer is granted "
"1 credit. After accumulating a specified amount of credits, the customer can "
"trade them in to receive (Y) item."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Купи X Получи Y`: за каждый купленный товар (X) клиент получает 1 "
"кредит. После накопления определенного количества кредитов клиент может "
"обменять их на получение товара (Y)."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/loyalty_discount.rst:112
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Next Order Coupons`: Generate and share single-use coupon codes "
"that grant access to rewards on the customer's next order."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Купоны на следующий заказ`: генерируйте и делитесь кодами купонов "
"для одноразового использования, которые предоставляют доступ к "
"вознаграждениям в следующем заказе клиента."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/loyalty_discount.rst:116
msgid "Conditional rules"
msgstr "Условные правила"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/loyalty_discount.rst:118
msgid ""
"Next, configure the :guilabel:`Conditional rules` that determine when the "
"program applies to a customer's order."
msgstr ""
"Затем настройте :guilabel:`Условные правила`, которые определяют, когда "
"программа применяется к заказу клиента."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/loyalty_discount.rst:121
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Rules & Rewards` tab, click :guilabel:`Add` next "
"to :guilabel:`Conditional rules` to add *conditions* to the program. This "
"reveals a :guilabel:`Create Conditional rules` pop-up window."
msgstr ""
"На вкладке :guilabel:`Правила и вознаграждения` нажмите :guilabel:`Добавить` "
"рядом с :guilabel:`Условные правила`, чтобы добавить *условия* к программе. "
"Откроется всплывающее окно :guilabel:`Создать условные правила`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/loyalty_discount.rst:None
msgid "Rules & Rewards tab of the loyalty program form."
msgstr "Вкладка «Правила и вознаграждения» формы программы лояльности."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/loyalty_discount.rst:130
msgid ""
"The options for :guilabel:`Conditional rules` vary depending on the "
"selected :ref:`Program Type <sales/pricing_management/program-types>`."
msgstr ""
"Параметры :guilabel:`Условных правил` различаются в зависимости от "
"выбранного :ref:`Типа программы <sales/pricing_management/program-types>`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/loyalty_discount.rst:133
msgid "The following options are available for configuring conditional rules:"
msgstr "Для настройки условных правил доступны следующие параметры:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/loyalty_discount.rst:135
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Discount Code`: Enter a custom code to be used for "
"the :guilabel:`Discount Code` program, or use the default one generated by "
"Odoo. This field is only available when the :guilabel:`Program Type` is set "
"to :guilabel:`Discount Code`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Код скидки`: введите пользовательский код для использования в "
"программе :guilabel:`Код скидки` или используйте код по умолчанию, "
"сгенерированный Odoo. Это поле доступно только в том случае, если "
":guilabel:`Тип программы` установлен на :guilabel:`Код скидки`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/loyalty_discount.rst:138
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Minimum Quantity`: Enter the minimum number of products that must "
"be purchased in order to access the reward. Set the minimum quantity to at "
"least `1` to ensure that the customer must make a purchase in order to "
"access the reward."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Минимальное количество`: введите минимальное количество товаров, "
"которые необходимо приобрести для получения вознаграждения. Установите "
"минимальное количество не менее `1`, чтобы клиент должен был совершить "
"покупку для получения вознаграждения."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/loyalty_discount.rst:141
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Minimum Purchase`: Enter the minimum amount (in currency), "
"with :guilabel:`tax Included` or :guilabel:`tax Excluded`, that must be "
"spent in order to access the reward. If both a minimum quantity *and* "
"minimum purchase amount are entered, then the customer's order must meet "
"both conditions."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Минимальная покупка`: введите минимальную сумму (в валюте), "
":guilabel:`с учетом налога` или :guilabel:`без учета налога`, которую "
"необходимо потратить для получения вознаграждения. Если введены как "
"минимальное количество, *так и* минимальная сумма покупки, то заказ клиента "
"должен соответствовать обоим условиям."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/loyalty_discount.rst:145
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Products`: Select the specific product(s) for which the program "
"applies. Leave this field blank to apply it to all products."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Товары`: выберите конкретные товары, к которым применяется "
"программа. Оставьте это поле пустым, чтобы применить её ко всем товарам."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/loyalty_discount.rst:147
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Categories`: Select the category of products for which the "
"program applies. Choose :guilabel:`All` to apply it to all product "
"categories."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Категории`: выберите категорию товаров, к которым применяется "
"программа. Выберите :guilabel:`Все`, чтобы применить её ко всем категориям "
"товаров."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/loyalty_discount.rst:149
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Product Tag:` Select a tag to apply the program to products with "
"that specific tag."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Тег товара:` выберите тег для применения программы к товарам с "
"этим конкретным тегом."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/loyalty_discount.rst:150
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Grant`: Enter the number of points the customer "
"earns :guilabel:`per order`, :guilabel:`per currency spent`, "
"or :guilabel:`per unit paid` (for the :guilabel:`Loyalty Cards` "
"and :guilabel:`Buy X Get Y` programs)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Начисление`: Введите количество баллов, которые клиент "
"зарабатывает :guilabel:`за заказ`, :guilabel:`за потраченную валюту` или "
":guilabel:`за оплаченную единицу` (для программ :guilabel:`Карты лояльности` "
"и :guilabel:`Купи X получи Y`)."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/loyalty_discount.rst:None
msgid ""
"Conditional rules configuration window for a discount or loyalty program."
msgstr "Окно настройки условных правил для программы скидок или лояльности."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/loyalty_discount.rst:158
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Save & Close` to save the rule and close the pop-up window, "
"or click :guilabel:`Save & New` to save the rule and immediately create a "
"new one."
msgstr ""
"Нажмите :guilabel:`Сохранить и закрыть`, чтобы сохранить правило и закрыть "
"всплывающее окно, или нажмите :guilabel:`Сохранить и создать`, чтобы "
"сохранить правило и сразу создать новое."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/loyalty_discount.rst:162
msgid "Rewards"
msgstr "Награды"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/loyalty_discount.rst:164
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Rules & Rewards` tab of the program form, "
"click :guilabel:`Add` next to :guilabel:`Rewards` to add *rewards* to the "
"program. This reveals a :guilabel:`Create Rewards` pop-up window."
msgstr ""
"На вкладке :guilabel:`Правила и вознаграждения` формы программы нажмите "
":guilabel:`Добавить` рядом с :guilabel:`Вознаграждения`, чтобы добавить "
"*вознаграждения* в программу. Откроется всплывающее окно :guilabel:`Создать "
"вознаграждения`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/loyalty_discount.rst:169
msgid ""
"The options for :guilabel:`Rewards` vary depending on the "
"selected :ref:`Program Type <sales/pricing_management/program-types>`."
msgstr ""
"Параметры для :guilabel:`Вознаграждения` различаются в зависимости от "
"выбранного :ref:`Типа программы <sales/pricing_management/program-types>`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/loyalty_discount.rst:172
msgid "The following options are available for configuring rewards:"
msgstr "Для настройки вознаграждений доступны следующие параметры:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/loyalty_discount.rst:174
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Reward Type`: Select the reward type among :guilabel:`Free "
"Product`, :guilabel:`Discount`, and :guilabel:`Free Shipping`. The other "
"options for reward configuration depend on the :guilabel:`Reward Type` "
"selected."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Тип вознаграждения`: Выберите тип вознаграждения среди "
":guilabel:`Бесплатный товар`, :guilabel:`Скидка` и :guilabel:`Бесплатная "
"доставка`. Другие параметры настройки вознаграждения зависят от выбранного "
":guilabel:`Типа вознаграждения`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/loyalty_discount.rst:178
msgid ":guilabel:`Free Product`:"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Бесплатный товар`:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/loyalty_discount.rst:180
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Quantity Rewarded`: Select the number of free products rewarded "
"to the customer."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Количество вознаграждения`: Выберите количество бесплатных "
"товаров, предоставляемых клиенту."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/loyalty_discount.rst:181
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Product`: Select the product given for free as a reward. Only one "
"product can be selected."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Товар`: Выберите товар, предоставляемый бесплатно в качестве "
"вознаграждения. Можно выбрать только один товар."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/loyalty_discount.rst:183
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Product Tag`: Select a tag to further specify the free product "
"eligible for the reward."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Метка товара`: Выберите метку для дополнительного уточнения "
"бесплатного товара, подходящего для вознаграждения."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/loyalty_discount.rst:186
msgid ":guilabel:`Discount`:"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Скидка`:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/loyalty_discount.rst:188
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Discount`: Enter the discounted amount in "
"either :guilabel:`percentage`, :guilabel:`currency per point`, "
"or :guilabel:`currency per order`. Then, select whether the discount applies "
"to the entire :guilabel:`Order`, only the :guilabel:`Cheapest Product` on "
"the order, or only :guilabel:`Specific Products`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/loyalty_discount.rst:192
#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/loyalty_discount.rst:197
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Max Discount`: Enter the maximum amount (in currency) that this "
"reward may grant as a discount. Leave this field at `0` for no limit."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Макс. скидка`: Введите максимальную сумму (в валюте), которую это "
"вознаграждение может предоставить в качестве скидки. Оставьте это поле "
"равным `0` для отсутствия ограничения."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/loyalty_discount.rst:195
msgid ":guilabel:`Free Shipping`:"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Бесплатная доставка`:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/loyalty_discount.rst:200
msgid ""
":guilabel:`In exchange of`: Enter the number of points required to exchange "
"for the reward (for the :guilabel:`Loyalty Cards` and :guilabel:`Buy X Get "
"Y` programs)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`В обмен на`: Введите количество баллов, необходимых для обмена на "
"вознаграждение (для программ :guilabel:`Карты лояльности` и :guilabel:`Купи "
"X получи Y`)."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/loyalty_discount.rst:202
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Description on order`: Enter the description of the reward, which "
"is displayed to the customer upon checkout."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Описание в заказе`: Введите описание вознаграждения, которое "
"отображается клиенту при оформлении заказа."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/loyalty_discount.rst:None
msgid "Rewards configuration window for a discount or loyalty program."
msgstr "Окно настройки вознаграждений для программы скидок или лояльности."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices.rst:5
msgid "Manage your pricing"
msgstr "Управляйте вашими ценами"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/currencies.rst:3
msgid "Foreign currencies"
msgstr "Иностранные валюты"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/currencies.rst:5
msgid ""
"With Odoo, pricelists can be used to manage prices in a number of foreign "
"currencies. Specifically, Odoo has the ability to work with 167 total "
"currencies."
msgstr ""
"С Odoo прайс-листы могут использоваться для управления ценами в нескольких "
"иностранных валютах. В частности, Odoo имеет возможность работать с 167 "
"валютами."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/currencies.rst:9
msgid ""
"In order to use multiple currencies in Odoo *Sales*, the *Accounting* "
"application **must** be installed."
msgstr ""
"Для использования нескольких валют в Odoo *Продажи* приложение "
"*Бухгалтерский учёт* **должно** быть установлено."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/currencies.rst:15
msgid ""
"Once the *Accounting* app has been installed, foreign currencies can be "
"added to the database. Navigate to :menuselection:`Accounting app --> "
"Configuration --> Settings`, scroll to the :guilabel:`Currencies` section, "
"and locate the :guilabel:`Main Currency` setting."
msgstr ""
"После установки приложения *Бухгалтерский учёт* в базу данных можно добавить "
"иностранные валюты. Перейдите в :menuselection:`Бухгалтерский учёт --> "
"Настройка --> Настройки`, прокрутите до раздела :guilabel:`Валюты` и найдите "
"настройку :guilabel:`Основная валюта`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/currencies.rst:None
msgid ""
"How the main currency feature appears on settings page in Odoo Accounting."
msgstr ""
"Как выглядит функция основной валюты на странице настроек Odoo Бухгалтерский "
"учёт."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/currencies.rst:23
msgid ""
"Odoo automatically sets the main currency as the currency of the country the "
"company is based in."
msgstr ""
"Odoo автоматически устанавливает основную валюту в соответствии с валютой "
"страны, в которой зарегистрирована компания."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/currencies.rst:25
msgid ""
"To change the main currency of the company, select the drop-down menu in "
"the :guilabel:`Currency` field, select the desired currency, and be sure "
"to :guilabel:`Save` the changes."
msgstr ""
"Чтобы изменить основную валюту компании, выберите раскрывающееся меню в поле "
":guilabel:`Валюта`, выберите нужную валюту и обязательно "
":guilabel:`Сохраните` изменения."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/currencies.rst:29
msgid ""
"To ensure currency rates are updated automatically, enable the *automatic "
"currency rates* feature on the *Accounting* settings page "
"(:menuselection:`Accounting app --> Configuration --> Settings --> "
"Currencies section`)."
msgstr ""
"Чтобы курсы валют обновлялись автоматически, включите функцию "
"*автоматического обновления курсов валют* на странице настроек модуля "
"*Бухгалтерский учёт* (:menuselection:`Бухгалтерский учёт --> Настройка --> "
"Настройки --> раздел Валюты`)."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/currencies.rst:37
msgid ""
"Click the checkbox beside the :guilabel:`Automatic Currency Rates` feature, "
"choose a designated bank to get the currency rates from in "
"the :guilabel:`Service` field drop-down menu, and select "
"an :guilabel:`Interval` of time for the updates to take place. Then "
"determine when the date of the :guilabel:`Next Run` should be."
msgstr ""
"Установите флажок рядом с функцией :guilabel:`Автоматические курсы валют`, "
"выберите в раскрывающемся меню поля :guilabel:`Сервис` банк для получения "
"курсов валют и выберите :guilabel:`Интервал` времени для обновления. Затем "
"укажите дату :guilabel:`Следующего запуска`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/currencies.rst:42
msgid ""
"To instantly update the currency rates, click the :guilabel:`🔁 (circular "
"arrows)` icon, located to the right of the :guilabel:`Next Run` field."
msgstr ""
"Чтобы мгновенно обновить курсы валют, нажмите значок :guilabel:`🔁 (круговые "
"стрелки)`, расположенный справа от поля :guilabel:`Следующий запуск`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/currencies.rst:45
msgid ""
"When all configurations are complete, be sure to :guilabel:`Save` all "
"changes."
msgstr ""
"После завершения всех настроек обязательно :guilabel:`Сохраните` все "
"изменения."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/currencies.rst:48
msgid ""
"All payment methods **must** be in the same currency as the sales journal, "
"or the company currency, if the company currency is not set. If it is not "
"the same, a :guilabel:`Validation Error` message appears."
msgstr ""
"Все способы оплаты **должны** быть в той же валюте, что и журнал продаж, или "
"в валюте компании, если валюта компании не установлена. Если валюта не "
"совпадает, появляется сообщение :guilabel:`Ошибка проверки`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/currencies.rst:53
msgid "View, edit, and add currencies"
msgstr "Просмотр, редактирование и добавление валют"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/currencies.rst:55
msgid ""
"To view, edit, and add currencies to the database, making them available on "
"pricelists and on the :guilabel:`Main Currency` drop-down menu, click "
"the :guilabel:`Currencies` link, located beneath the :guilabel:`Currency` "
"field on the :menuselection:`Accounting app --> Settings` page."
msgstr ""
"Чтобы просмотреть, отредактировать и добавить валюты в базу данных, сделав "
"их доступными в прайс-листах и в раскрывающемся меню :guilabel:`Основная "
"валюта`, нажмите ссылку :guilabel:`Валюты`, расположенную под полем "
":guilabel:`Валюта` на странице :menuselection:`Бухгалтерский учёт --> "
"Настройки`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/currencies.rst:59
msgid ""
"When the :guilabel:`Currencies` link is clicked, a "
"separate :guilabel:`Currencies` page is revealed."
msgstr ""
"При нажатии на ссылку :guilabel:`Валюты` открывается отдельная страница "
":guilabel:`Валюты`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/currencies.rst:None
msgid "How the main currencies page appears in Odoo Accounting."
msgstr "Как выглядит страница основных валют в Odoo Бухгалтерский учёт."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/currencies.rst:65
msgid ""
"On this page, Odoo provides a master list of 167 global currencies. Each row "
"shows the "
"corresponding :guilabel:`Currency`, :guilabel:`Symbol`, :guilabel:`Name`, "
"date of the :guilabel:`Last Update`, and :guilabel:`Current Rate` (compared "
"to the default currency of the country in which the company is based)."
msgstr ""
"На этой странице Odoo предоставляет основной список из 167 мировых валют. В "
"каждой строке указаны соответствующие :guilabel:`Валюта`, "
":guilabel:`Символ`, :guilabel:`Название`, дата :guilabel:`Последнего "
"обновления` и :guilabel:`Текущий курс` (по сравнению с валютой по умолчанию "
"страны, в которой зарегистрирована компания)."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/currencies.rst:70
msgid ""
"To the far right, there are two columns, which can be toggled on or off:"
msgstr "Справа расположены два столбца, которые можно включать и выключать:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/currencies.rst:72
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Use on eBay`: this currency can be used with the connected eBay "
"account (if applicable)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/currencies.rst:74
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Active`: this currency is activated, which means it can be added "
"to a pricelist, or used as the main currency of the company, if desired "
"(via :menuselection:`Accounting app --> Configuration --> Settings --> "
"Currencies section`)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Активна`: эта валюта активирована, что означает, что её можно "
"добавить в прайс-лист или использовать в качестве основной валюты компании "
"при необходимости (через :menuselection:`Бухгалтерский учёт --> "
"Настройка --> Настройки --> раздел Валюты`)."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/currencies.rst:79
msgid ""
"By default, all the :guilabel:`Active` currency options are at the top of "
"the list."
msgstr ""
"По умолчанию все варианты :guilabel:`Активных` валют находятся в верхней "
"части списка."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/currencies.rst:82
msgid ""
"It is recommended that *at least* one pricelist is created "
"per :guilabel:`Active` currency. See :doc:`./pricing` to learn more about "
"pricelist configuration."
msgstr ""
"Рекомендуется создать *как минимум* один прайс-лист для каждой "
":guilabel:`Активной` валюты. См. :doc:`./pricing`, чтобы узнать больше о "
"настройке прайс-листов."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/currencies.rst:85
msgid ""
"To toggle options on/off, click the toggle switch in the row for the "
"corresponding column. When *on* the color of the switch is green. When "
"*off*, the color of the switch is grey."
msgstr ""
"Чтобы включить или выключить параметры, нажмите переключатель в строке "
"соответствующего столбца. Когда переключатель *включен*, его цвет зелёный. "
"Когда *выключен*, его цвет серый."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/currencies.rst:89
msgid "Currency detail form"
msgstr "Форма сведений о валюте"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/currencies.rst:91
msgid ""
"To edit any currency on the :guilabel:`Currencies` page, click the desired "
"currency to reveal the detail form for that specific currency, and proceed "
"to make any necessary changes."
msgstr ""
"Чтобы изменить любую валюту на странице :guilabel:`Валюты`, нажмите на "
"нужную валюту, чтобы открыть форму с подробной информацией об этой "
"конкретной валюте, и внесите необходимые изменения."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/currencies.rst:None
msgid "How a currency detail form looks in Odoo Accounting."
msgstr ""
"Как выглядит форма с подробной информацией о валюте в Odoo Бухгалтерский "
"учёт."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/currencies.rst:98
msgid ""
"On the currency detail form, the relevant currency code appears in "
"the :guilabel:`Currency` field. Beneath that, the name for the currency is "
"in the :guilabel:`Name` field."
msgstr ""
"В форме с подробной информацией о валюте соответствующий код валюты "
"отображается в поле :guilabel:`Валюта`. Под ним находится название валюты в "
"поле :guilabel:`Название`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/currencies.rst:101
msgid ""
"Then, toggle the currency's availability with the :guilabel:`Active` toggle: "
"*on* is indicated with a green switch, and *off* is indicated with a grey "
"switch."
msgstr ""
"Затем переключите доступность валюты с помощью переключателя "
":guilabel:`Активно`: состояние *включено* обозначается зелёным "
"переключателем, а состояние *выключено* — серым переключателем."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/currencies.rst:104
msgid ""
"On the right of the currency detail form, the "
"appropriate :guilabel:`Currency Unit` (e.g. `Dollars`) "
"and :guilabel:`Currency Subunit` (e.g. `Cents`) can be found."
msgstr ""
"Справа на форме с подробной информацией о валюте можно найти соответствующую "
":guilabel:`Единицу валюты` (например, `доллары`) и :guilabel:`Подъединицу "
"валюты` (например, `центы`)."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/currencies.rst:107
msgid ""
"If the currency is meant to be used for eBay purposes, toggle "
"the :guilabel:`Use on eBay` option to the desired activation."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/currencies.rst:110
msgid ""
"Next, under the :guilabel:`Rates` tab, the various conversion rates can be "
"viewed, added, or deleted. Each row shows the :guilabel:`Date` of that "
"specific rate, the :guilabel:`Company` to which it is connected, followed by "
"the :guilabel:`Unit per...` and :guilabel:`...per Unit`."
msgstr ""
"Далее на вкладке :guilabel:`Курсы` можно просмотреть, добавить или удалить "
"различные курсы конвертации. В каждой строке отображается :guilabel:`Дата` "
"этого конкретного курса, :guilabel:`Компания`, к которой он относится, а "
"затем :guilabel:`Единиц в...` и :guilabel:`...за единицу`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/currencies.rst:115
#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/currencies.rst:166
msgid ""
"The *...* in each of the last two columns represents the main currency set "
"for the company. For example, if the main currency is set to `USD`, the "
"columns are titled :guilabel:`Unit per USD` and :guilabel:`USD per Unit`."
msgstr ""
"Символ *...* в каждом из последних двух столбцов обозначает основную валюту, "
"установленную для компании. Например, если основной валютой установлен "
"`USD`, столбцы называются :guilabel:`Единиц в USD` и :guilabel:`USD за "
"единицу`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/currencies.rst:119
msgid ""
"To add a new rate, click :guilabel:`Add a line` in the :guilabel:`Rates` "
"tab, and proceed to fill in the necessary information in the aforementioned "
"columns."
msgstr ""
"Чтобы добавить новый курс, нажмите :guilabel:`Добавить строку` на вкладке "
":guilabel:`Курсы` и заполните необходимую информацию в указанных столбцах."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/currencies.rst:123
msgid "Main currency detail form"
msgstr "Форма основной валюты с подробной информацией"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/currencies.rst:125
msgid ""
"If the selected currency is the main currency of the company, a blue banner "
"appears at the top of the currency detail form with the "
"message: :guilabel:`This is your company's currency.`."
msgstr ""
"Если выбранная валюта является основной валютой компании, в верхней части "
"формы с подробной информацией о валюте появляется синий баннер с сообщением: "
":guilabel:`Это валюта вашей компании.`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/currencies.rst:None
msgid "How a main currency detail form looks in Odoo Accounting."
msgstr ""
"Как выглядит форма с подробной информацией об основной валюте в Odoo "
"Бухгалтерский учёт."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/currencies.rst:132
msgid ""
"All the fields are the same as a typical currency detail form, but there "
"will **not** be a :guilabel:`Rates` tab because all other currency rates are "
"based off the main currency of the company."
msgstr ""
"Все поля такие же, как в обычной форме с подробной информацией о валюте, но "
"вкладки :guilabel:`Курсы` **не** будет, поскольку все остальные курсы валют "
"основаны на основной валюте компании."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/currencies.rst:137
msgid "Create new currency"
msgstr "Создать новую валюту"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/currencies.rst:139
msgid ""
"If a desired currency isn't on the :guilabel:`Currencies` page, click "
"the :guilabel:`New` button to open a blank currency template form."
msgstr ""
"Если нужной валюты нет на странице :guilabel:`Валюты`, нажмите кнопку "
":guilabel:`Создать`, чтобы открыть пустую форму шаблона валюты."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/currencies.rst:143
msgid ""
"The same :guilabel:`New` button is located in the upper-right corner of any "
"currency detail form."
msgstr ""
"Та же кнопка :guilabel:`Создать` находится в правом верхнем углу любой формы "
"с подробной информацией о валюте."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/currencies.rst:None
msgid "How a blank currency detail form looks in Odoo Accounting."
msgstr ""
"Как выглядит пустая форма с подробной информацией о валюте в Odoo "
"Бухгалтерский учёт."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/currencies.rst:149
msgid ""
"On the blank currency detail form, proceed to enter the desired currency "
"code in the :guilabel:`Currency` field. Beneath that, enter the name for the "
"currency in the :guilabel:`Name` field."
msgstr ""
"В пустой форме с подробной информацией о валюте введите нужный код валюты в "
"поле :guilabel:`Валюта`. Под ним введите название валюты в поле "
":guilabel:`Название`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/currencies.rst:153
msgid ""
"Then, toggle the currency's availability with the :guilabel:`Active` toggle "
"switch."
msgstr ""
"Затем переключите доступность валюты с помощью переключателя "
":guilabel:`Активно`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/currencies.rst:155
msgid ""
"On the right of the currency detail form, enter the "
"appropriate :guilabel:`Currency Unit` (e.g. `Dollars`) and "
"appropriate :guilabel:`Currency Subunit` (e.g. `Cents`)."
msgstr ""
"Справа на форме с подробной информацией о валюте введите соответствующую "
":guilabel:`Единицу валюты` (например, `доллары`) и соответствующую "
":guilabel:`Подъединицу валюты` (например, `центы`)."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/currencies.rst:158
msgid ""
"If the currency is meant to be used for eBay purposes, toggle "
"the :guilabel:`Use on eBay` to the desired activation."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/currencies.rst:161
msgid ""
"Next, under the :guilabel:`Rates` tab, add a new rate by "
"clicking :guilabel:`Add a line`. Then, proceed to confirm and adjust "
"the :guilabel:`Date`, :guilabel:`Company`, :guilabel:`Unit per...`, "
"and :guilabel:`...per Unit` fields to ensure all the auto-populated "
"information is accurate."
msgstr ""
"Далее на вкладке :guilabel:`Курсы` добавьте новый курс, нажав "
":guilabel:`Добавить строку`. Затем подтвердите и откорректируйте поля "
":guilabel:`Дата`, :guilabel:`Компания`, :guilabel:`Единиц в...` и "
":guilabel:`...за единицу`, чтобы убедиться, что вся автоматически "
"заполненная информация верна."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/currencies.rst:171
msgid "Currency-specific pricelists"
msgstr "Прайс-листы для конкретных валют"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/currencies.rst:173
msgid ""
"It is recommended that *at least* one pricelist is created per active "
"currency in the database. To create (or assign) a pricelist to a specific "
"currency, start by navigating to :menuselection:`Sales app --> Products --> "
"Pricelists`."
msgstr ""
"Рекомендуется создать *как минимум* один прайс-лист для каждой активной "
"валюты в базе данных. Чтобы создать (или назначить) прайс-лист для "
"конкретной валюты, начните с перехода в :menuselection:`Продажи --> "
"Продукты --> Прайс-листы`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/currencies.rst:177
msgid ""
"From the :guilabel:`Pricelists` page, either select an existing pricelist to "
"edit, or click :guilabel:`New` to create a new pricelist."
msgstr ""
"На странице :guilabel:`Прайс-листы` либо выберите существующий прайс-лист "
"для редактирования, либо нажмите :guilabel:`Создать`, чтобы создать новый "
"прайс-лист."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/currencies.rst:180
msgid ""
"On the pricelist detail form, for either a new or existing pricelist, adjust "
"the :guilabel:`Currency` field as desired."
msgstr ""
"В форме сведений о прайс-листе, будь то новый или существующий прайс-лист, "
"настройте поле :guilabel:`Валюта` по желанию."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/currencies.rst:184
msgid ":doc:`./pricing` to learn more about pricelist configuration."
msgstr ":doc:`./pricing`, чтобы узнать больше о настройке прайс-листа."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/currencies.rst:187
msgid "Auto-conversion from public price"
msgstr "Автоматическое преобразование из публичной цены"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/currencies.rst:189
msgid ""
"It should be noted that the public price seen on products is directly "
"related to the main currency the company has set, which is configured by "
"navigating to :menuselection:`Accounting app --> Configuration --> Settings "
"--> Currencies section --> Main Currency --> Currency drop-down menu`."
msgstr ""
"Следует отметить, что публичная цена, отображаемая на продуктах, напрямую "
"связана с основной валютой, установленной для компании, которая "
"настраивается путем перехода в :menuselection:`Бухгалтерский учёт --> "
"Конфигурация --> Настройки --> раздел Валюты --> Основная валюта --> "
"выпадающее меню Валюта`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/currencies.rst:193
msgid ""
"The sales price automatically updates if the pricelist is changed to a "
"different pricelist that has a different currency than the company's main "
"currency. The change in price is directly related to the updated conversion "
"rate for that currency."
msgstr ""
"Цена продажи автоматически обновляется, если прайс-лист изменяется на другой "
"прайс-лист, который имеет валюту, отличную от основной валюты компании. "
"Изменение цены напрямую связано с обновленным курсом конвертации для этой "
"валюты."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/currencies.rst:198
msgid "Set product prices"
msgstr "Установка цен на продукты"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/currencies.rst:200
msgid ""
"In order to have product prices set in place to avoid any changes in "
"currency rates, start by navigating to :menuselection:`Sales app --> "
"Products --> Products`."
msgstr ""
"Чтобы установить цены на продукты и избежать каких-либо изменений курсов "
"валют, начните с перехода в :menuselection:`Продажи --> Продукты --> "
"Продукты`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/currencies.rst:203
msgid ""
"From the :guilabel:`Products` page, select the desired product to modify. "
"Or, create a new product by clicking the :guilabel:`New` button."
msgstr ""
"На странице :guilabel:`Продукты` выберите желаемый продукт для изменения. "
"Или создайте новый продукт, нажав кнопку :guilabel:`Создать`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/currencies.rst:206
msgid ""
"Then, on the product detail form, click the :guilabel:`Extra Prices` smart "
"button, located in the upper-left corner. Doing so reveals a "
"separate :guilabel:`Price Rules` page, specific to that particular product."
msgstr ""
"Затем в форме сведений о продукте нажмите смарт-кнопку "
":guilabel:`Дополнительные цены`, расположенную в верхнем левом углу. Это "
"откроет отдельную страницу :guilabel:`Правила цен`, специфичную для этого "
"конкретного продукта."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/currencies.rst:None
msgid ""
"How to set product prices based on foreign currency pricelists in Odoo Sales."
msgstr ""
"Как установить цены на продукты на основе прайс-листов в иностранной валюте "
"в Odoo Продажи."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/currencies.rst:214
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`New`, and select the desired pricelist from the drop-down "
"menu in the :guilabel:`Pricelist` column."
msgstr ""
"Нажмите :guilabel:`Создать` и выберите желаемый прайс-лист из выпадающего "
"меню в столбце :guilabel:`Прайс-лист`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/currencies.rst:217
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Applied On` field is auto-populated with the product, so "
"proceed to enter in the desired figures in the :guilabel:`Min. Quantity` "
"and :guilabel:`Price` fields."
msgstr ""
"Поле :guilabel:`Применяется к` автоматически заполняется продуктом, поэтому "
"переходите к вводу желаемых значений в поля :guilabel:`Мин. количество` и "
":guilabel:`Цена`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/currencies.rst:221
msgid ""
"The figure in the :guilabel:`Min. Quantity` field means "
"the :guilabel:`Price` being set will **only** trigger if at least that "
"amount of product is purchased."
msgstr ""
"Значение в поле :guilabel:`Мин. количество` означает, что устанавливаемая "
":guilabel:`Цена` сработает **только** в том случае, если будет приобретено "
"как минимум такое количество продукта."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/currencies.rst:224
msgid ""
"If necessary, configure a :guilabel:`Start Date` and :guilabel:`End Date` "
"for the set prices. Leaving those columns blank ensures the set price will "
"remain valid, regardless of the date of sale."
msgstr ""
"При необходимости настройте :guilabel:`Дата начала` и :guilabel:`Дата "
"окончания` для установленных цен. Оставление этих столбцов пустыми "
"гарантирует, что установленная цена останется действительной независимо от "
"даты продажи."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/currencies.rst:227
msgid ""
"If working in a multi-company environment, designate to which company this "
"price rule should be applied in the :guilabel:`Company` field. Leaving that "
"field blank ensures the price rule applies to all companies in the database."
msgstr ""
"Если вы работаете в мультикомпанийной среде, укажите, к какой компании "
"должно применяться это правило цены, в поле :guilabel:`Компания`. Оставление "
"этого поля пустым гарантирует, что правило цены применяется ко всем "
"компаниям в базе данных."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/currencies.rst:231
msgid ""
"With those configurations complete, regardless of any changes/updates in "
"conversion, whenever those designated pricelists are applied to a customer "
"trying to purchase this specific product, these pre-determined set prices "
"appear."
msgstr ""
"После завершения этих настроек, независимо от каких-либо изменений/"
"обновлений курса конвертации, когда эти указанные прайс-листы применяются к "
"клиенту, пытающемуся приобрести этот конкретный продукт, появляются эти "
"заранее определенные установленные цены."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/currencies.rst:236
msgid ":doc:`./pricing`"
msgstr ":doc:`./pricing`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:3
msgid "Pricelists, discounts, and formulas"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:5
msgid ""
"Odoo *Sales* has a useful pricelist feature that can be tailored to fit any "
"unique pricing strategy."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:7
msgid ""
"A *pricelist* is a list of prices (or price rules) that Odoo uses to "
"determine the appropriate price for a customer. These pricelists can be set "
"with specific criteria (such as time periods, minimum quantity sold, and "
"more) in order to apply certain prices or discounts."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:11
msgid ""
"Pricelists suggest certain prices, but they can always be overridden on the "
"sales order."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:14
msgid "Pricing strategy options"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:16
msgid ""
"To choose a pricing strategy, first navigate to :menuselection:`Sales app --"
"> Configuration --> Settings`. In the :guilabel:`Pricing` section, click the "
"checkbox next to the :guilabel:`Pricelists` feature."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:20
msgid ""
"Doing so reveals two additional options beneath it: :guilabel:`Multiple "
"prices per product` and :guilabel:`Advanced price rules (discounts, "
"formulas)`. A link labeled :guilabel:`Pricelists` also appears, which leads "
"to a separate pricelists page, wherein pricelists can be created and/or "
"modified."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:25
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Multiple prices per product`: provides the option to set several "
"different prices per product."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:27
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Advanced price rules (discounts, formulas)`: provides the option "
"to create detailed price rules and apply discounts, margins, and roundings."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:None
msgid "How the pricelist feature setting looks in Odoo Sales."
msgstr "Как выглядит настройка функции прайс-листов в Odoo Продажи."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:33
msgid ""
"After clicking the checkbox beside the :guilabel:`Pricelists` feature, "
"select one of those two options, then click :guilabel:`Save` to save all "
"changes."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:41
msgid ""
"After activating and saving the :guilabel:`Pricelists` feature, "
"the :guilabel:`Settings` page reloads and, from here, either select "
"the :guilabel:`Pricelists` link (beneath the :guilabel:`Pricelists` feature "
"on the :guilabel:`Settings` page), or navigate to :menuselection:`Sales app "
"--> Products --> Pricelists`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:46
#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:418
msgid ""
"Either option reveals the :guilabel:`Pricelists` page, in which pricelists "
"can be created and/or modified at any time."
msgstr ""
"Любой из вариантов открывает страницу :guilabel:`Прайс-листы`, на которой "
"прайс-листы могут быть созданы и/или изменены в любое время."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:None
msgid "How the pricelists page looks in Odoo Sales."
msgstr "Как выглядит страница прайс-листов в Odoo Продажи."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:53
msgid ""
"The order of the pricelists on the :guilabel:`Pricelists` page has an impact "
"on how they are applied. If several pricelists share the same criteria, "
"**only** the first listed pricelist is applied."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:57
msgid ""
"For example, for two pricelists with different rules, but same criteria "
"(e.g., same website, same country), only the *first* pricelist in the list "
"is applied."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:61
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Public Pricelist` is the default pricelist used with Odoo "
"*Sales* and *eCommerce*. This pricelist is applied by default, if there are "
"no matching criteria."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:64
msgid ""
"From the :guilabel:`Pricelists` page, either select the desired pricelist to "
"edit, or click :guilabel:`New` to create a new pricelist, which reveals a "
"blank pricelist form that can be configured in a number of different ways."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:None
msgid "How the pricelist detail form looks in Odoo Sales."
msgstr "Как выглядит детальная форма прайс-листа в Odoo Продажи."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:71
msgid ""
"When creating a new pricelist, start by adding a name for the pricelist at "
"the top of the form, in the blank field. Next, select "
"which :guilabel:`Currency` should be used."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:74
msgid ""
"Then, if working in a multi-company environment, select which company this "
"pricelist should apply to in the :guilabel:`Company` field. If this field is "
"left blank, the pricelist is automatically applied to all companies in the "
"database."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:79
msgid "Price Rules tab"
msgstr "Вкладка ценовых правил"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:81
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Price Rules` tab functionality on a pricelist form varies "
"depending on the :guilabel:`Pricelists` setting chosen: "
"either :guilabel:`Multiple prices per product` or :guilabel:`Advanced price "
"rules (discounts, formulas)`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:85
msgid ""
"However, the :guilabel:`Time-based rules` tab and :guilabel:`Configuration` "
"tab are always the same, regardless of the chosen :guilabel:`Pricelists` "
"setting."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:91
msgid ""
"With the :guilabel:`Multiple prices per product` setting activated, "
"the :guilabel:`Price Rules` tab on pricelist forms provides the option to "
"add specific products, with a specific price, to a pricelist."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:95
msgid ""
"To add a specific product and price to a pricelist form, click "
"the :guilabel:`Price Rules` tab, then click :guilabel:`Add a line` in "
"the :guilabel:`Products` column. Then, select the desired product for which "
"a specific price should be applied."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:99
msgid ""
"Next, if necessary, select a product variant under the :guilabel:`Variants` "
"column (e.g. a specific product size, color, etc.). If no variants are "
"selected, then this price will apply to all variants of the product."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:103
msgid ""
"If a minimum amount of the product must be purchased in order to apply the "
"specific price, enter the amount under the :guilabel:`Min. Quantity` column."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:106
msgid ""
"To configure the price of the product for this specific pricelist, enter the "
"desired amount under the :guilabel:`Price` column. Then, there is the option "
"to add a :guilabel:`Start Date` and :guilabel:`End Date` to the configured "
"product price, if desired."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:110
msgid ""
"To add another product line, click :guilabel:`Add a line` again, and repeat "
"the process. There is no limit to how many products can be added in "
"the :guilabel:`Price Rules` tab of a pricelist form."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:113
msgid ""
"For more information, check out the following section: :ref:`Multiple prices "
"per product <sales/multiple-prices-per-product>`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:119
msgid ""
"With the :guilabel:`Advanced price rules (discounts, formulas)` setting "
"activated, the :guilabel:`Price Rules` tab on pricelist forms provides the "
"option to configure detailed price rules based on formulas."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:123
msgid ""
"Check out the :ref:`Advanced price rules (discounts, formulas) <sales/"
"advanced-price-rules>` section for detailed steps on how to add advanced "
"price rules to a pricelist."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:127
msgid "Recurring Prices tab"
msgstr "Вкладка Повторяющиеся цены"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:129
msgid ""
"Time-based rules are used specifically with subscription products. Be sure "
"to check out the Odoo :doc:`Subscriptions </applications/sales/"
"subscriptions>` documentation for more information."
msgstr ""
"Правила на основе времени используются специально для продуктов подписки. "
"Обязательно ознакомьтесь с документацией Odoo :doc:`Подписки </applications/"
"sales/subscriptions>` для получения дополнительной информации."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:132
msgid ""
"Under the :guilabel:`Recurring Prices` tab, the same functionality of "
"the :guilabel:`Price Rules` tab is present. The only difference being that a "
"recurring time period can be applied in the :guilabel:`Recurring Plan` "
"column."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:136
msgid ""
"Once :guilabel:`Products` and/or :guilabel:`Product Variants` are selected, "
"click :guilabel:`Add a price rule`, and select the blank field in "
"the :guilabel:`Recurring Plan` column to reveal a drop-down menu of pre-"
"designated recurrence periods (e.g. `Monthly`, `Quarterly`, `Weekly`, etc.)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:140
msgid ""
"New recurrence periods can also be created from this column. To do so, type "
"in the name for the new :guilabel:`Recurring Plan`, then "
"select :guilabel:`Create` from the resulting drop-down menu to create the "
"time period, which can be edited later."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:144
msgid ""
"Or, select :guilabel:`Create and edit...` to reveal a :guilabel:`Create "
"Recurring Plan` pop-up form. From this pop-up form, the new recurrence "
"period can be configured, with specific :guilabel:`Details`, :guilabel:`Self-"
"Service`, and :guilabel:`Pricing` options. When the configurations are "
"complete, click the :guilabel:`Save & Close` button."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:None
msgid "Custom time period pop-up form in Odoo Sales."
msgstr "Всплывающая форма пользовательского периода времени в Odoo Продажи."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:152
msgid ""
"Lastly, add the desired price for this recurring price rule in "
"the :guilabel:`Recurring Price` column."
msgstr ""
"Наконец, добавьте желаемую цену для этого правила регулярной цены в столбце "
":guilabel:`Recurring Price`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:156
msgid ":doc:`../../../subscriptions`"
msgstr ":doc:`../../../subscriptions`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:159
msgid "Rental rules tab"
msgstr "Вкладка правил аренды"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:161
msgid ""
"Under the :guilabel:`Rental rules` tab, specific price rules can be "
"configured for various rental products, using the same methodology as "
"the :guilabel:`Price Rules` and :guilabel:`Recurring Prices` tabs."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:165
msgid ""
"To add a rental rule, click :guilabel:`Add a line`, and select a desired "
"product in the :guilabel:`Products` column. Then, select any "
"specific :guilabel:`Variants`, if necessary."
msgstr ""
"Чтобы добавить правило аренды, нажмите :guilabel:`Add a line` и выберите "
"нужный продукт в столбце :guilabel:`Products`. Затем выберите любые "
"конкретные :guilabel:`Variants`, если необходимо."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:168
msgid ""
"Next, designate a :guilabel:`Period` of time for the rental rule (e.g. "
"`Daily`, `Hourly`, etc.)."
msgstr ""
"Далее укажите :guilabel:`Period` времени для правила аренды (например, "
"`Daily`, `Hourly` и т. д.)."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:170
msgid ""
"Lastly, configure a :guilabel:`Price` for the rental rule in the respective "
"column."
msgstr ""
"Наконец, настройте :guilabel:`Price` для правила аренды в соответствующем "
"столбце."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:173
msgid "Configuration tab"
msgstr "Вкладка конфигурации"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:175
msgid ""
"Under the :guilabel:`Configuration` tab, there are a few options that can "
"further customize the pricelist."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:None
msgid "Configuration tab on pricelist detail form in Odoo Sales."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:181
msgid ""
"From here, under the :guilabel:`Availability` section, in "
"the :guilabel:`Country Groups` field, certain country groups can be added to "
"the pricelist. There is no limit to how many country groups can be added in "
"this field."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:186
msgid ""
"If no country is set for a customer, Odoo takes the first pricelist without "
"any country group."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:188
msgid ""
"Under the :guilabel:`Website` section, there are a few options that can be "
"configured. In the :guilabel:`Website` field, this pricelist can be applied "
"to a specific website, if working in a multi-website environment. If left "
"blank, the pricelist is applied to all websites in the database."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:192
msgid ""
"Tick the :guilabel:`Selectable` checkbox to have this pricelist as a "
"selectable option for customers to choose as they shop. If "
"the :guilabel:`Selectable` box is left unticked, customers **cannot** select "
"this pricelist for themselves."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:196
msgid ""
"Lastly, there is the option to add an :guilabel:`E-commerce Promotional "
"Code`. To add a code, type in the desired promo code that, when entered "
"during the checkout process, applies the pricelist to the customer, even if "
"the customer does not fall into the previously-specified criteria."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:203
msgid "Show discount percentage to customers"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:205
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Discounts` section, there is a :guilabel:`Discount Policy` "
"label with two radio options to choose from: :guilabel:`Discount included in "
"the price` or :guilabel:`Show public price & discount to the customer`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:209
msgid ""
"If :guilabel:`Discount included in the price` is selected, the price shown "
"to the customer already accounts for the discount being applied. However, "
"if :guilabel:`Show public price & discount to the customer` is selected, the "
"customer sees the actual public price *and* how much they are saving with "
"this pricelist discount."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:215
msgid "Customer pricelist application"
msgstr "Применение прайс-листа клиента"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:217
msgid ""
"While the default pricelist applied to any customer is the :guilabel:`Public "
"Pricelist`, Odoo provides the opportunity to directly apply a different "
"pricelist to customers on their contact form."
msgstr ""
"Хотя прайс-листом по умолчанию, применяемым к любому клиенту, является "
":guilabel:`Public Pricelist`, Odoo предоставляет возможность напрямую "
"применить другой прайс-лист к клиентам в их контактной форме."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:220
msgid ""
"To do that, open the desired customer's contact form, either by navigating "
"to :menuselection:`Sales app --> Orders --> Customers` and selecting the "
"customer from the main :guilabel:`Customers` page, or by clicking on the "
"customer's name on a sales order."
msgstr ""
"Для этого откройте контактную форму нужного клиента, перейдя в "
":menuselection:`Sales app --> Orders --> Customers` и выбрав клиента на "
"главной странице :guilabel:`Customers`, или нажав на имя клиента в заказе на "
"продажу."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:None
msgid "Sample customer detail form in Odoo Sales."
msgstr "Образец формы данных клиента в Odoo Продажи."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:227
msgid ""
"On the desired customer's contact form, under the :guilabel:`Sales & "
"Purchase` tab, in the :guilabel:`Sales` section, designate what pricelist "
"should be applied to this specific customer from the drop-down menu in "
"the :guilabel:`Pricelist` field."
msgstr ""
"В контактной форме нужного клиента на вкладке :guilabel:`Sales & Purchase` в "
"разделе :guilabel:`Sales` укажите, какой прайс-лист должен быть применен к "
"этому конкретному клиенту, выбрав его из выпадающего меню в поле "
":guilabel:`Pricelist`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:None
msgid "The pricelist field in a customer detail form in Odoo Sales."
msgstr "Поле прайс-листа в форме данных клиента в Odoo Продажи."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:235
msgid ""
"When a customer is added to the database, the default pricelist is "
"automatically applied to them. There is **no way** to have a blank "
"*Pricelist* field on a contact form. Even if that field is left blank, the "
"default pricelist appears when that contact form is opened again."
msgstr ""
"Когда клиент добавляется в базу данных, к нему автоматически применяется "
"прайс-лист по умолчанию. **Невозможно** оставить поле *Прайс-лист* пустым в "
"форме контакта. Даже если это поле оставить пустым, прайс-лист по умолчанию "
"появится при повторном открытии этой формы контакта."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:239
msgid ""
"However, when that contact is added to a quotation, and the *Pricelist* "
"field is auto-populated (based on the information from their contact form), "
"that predetermined pricelist can be removed from the *Pricelist* field, and "
"the quotation can still be confirmed, and subsequently, turned into a sales "
"order."
msgstr ""
"Однако, когда этот контакт добавляется в коммерческое предложение, и поле "
"*Прайс-лист* автоматически заполняется (на основе информации из формы "
"контакта), этот предопределенный прайс-лист можно удалить из поля *Прайс-"
"лист*, и коммерческое предложение все равно можно подтвердить и впоследствии "
"превратить в заказ на продажу."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:249
msgid ""
"To apply several prices per individual product, select "
"the :guilabel:`Multiple prices per product` option, after enabling "
"the :guilabel:`Pricelists` feature on the *Sales* app setting page "
"(:menuselection:`Sales app --> Configuration --> Settings`), and "
"click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:253
msgid ""
"Next, apply pricelists to specific products using the product form. Navigate "
"to the :menuselection:`Sales app --> Products --> Products` and select the "
"product for which multiple prices should be applied. Selecting a product "
"from the :guilabel:`Products` page reveals that specific product's product "
"form on a separate page."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:258
msgid ""
"On the product form, click the :guilabel:`Extra Prices` smart button, "
"located at the top of the form."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:None
msgid "How the extra prices smart button appears in Odoo Sales."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:264
msgid ""
"Doing so reveals a separate page displaying the :guilabel:`Price Rules` that "
"are specific to that particular product. Here, price rules can be edited or "
"created at any time."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:None
msgid "How the extra price rules per product page appears in Odoo Sales."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:270
msgid ""
"To create a new price rule for a product from this specific :guilabel:`Price "
"Rules` page, click :guilabel:`New` to add a new, customizable row that has "
"the desired product already populated in the :guilabel:`Applied On` column."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:274
msgid ""
"Next, select which :guilabel:`Pricelist` this specific product price rule "
"should apply to, via the drop-down menu in the :guilabel:`Pricelist` column."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:278
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Public Pricelist` is the default pricelist used with Odoo "
"*Sales* and *eCommerce*."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:281
msgid ""
"To create a new pricelist from this page, type in the desired name of the "
"new pricelist in the :guilabel:`Pricelist` column, then "
"select :guilabel:`Create` from the drop-down menu. All pricelists can be "
"modified at any time, by navigating to :menuselection:`Sales app --> "
"Products --> Pricelists`. Pricelists can also be created on that "
"specific :guilabel:`Pricelists` page, as well."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:287
msgid ""
"After the desired pricelist is added to the row, designate a :guilabel:`Min. "
"Quantity` for the price rule."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:291
msgid ""
"If the :guilabel:`Min. Quantity` column is set to `2`, the new price in "
"the :guilabel:`Price` column will be applied to orders of 2 or more "
"products. So, in theory, if a single product costs $100, customers can be "
"encouraged to buy more, if the :guilabel:`Price` is set at $85 per product "
"for a :guilabel:`Min. Quantity` of `2` products."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:296
msgid ""
"Next, enter the desired amount in the :guilabel:`Price` column. Then, if "
"needed, enter a :guilabel:`Start Date` and :guilabel:`End Date` for the "
"product's price rule."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:299
msgid ""
"And lastly, if working in a multi-company environment, select which company "
"this price rule should be applied to in the :guilabel:`Company` field. "
"Leaving this field blank means the price rule applies for all companies in "
"the database."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:303
msgid ""
"Click away from the row to activate Odoo's auto-save capability, meaning "
"that newly-created price rule is now ready to be used."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:306
msgid ""
"Proceed to add as many unique price rules per product as desired. There is "
"no limit to how many price rules can be added per product."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:309
msgid ""
"With the price rule(s) in place for a specific product, customers who fall "
"into those corresponding pricelists automatically see those new prices "
"applied. The number of price rules applied to a particular product are also "
"displayed in the :guilabel:`Extra Prices` smart button, located on every "
"product form."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:315
msgid ""
"When a price rule/pricelist is added to a product via the :guilabel:`Extra "
"Prices` smart button, it is also reflected on the pricelist itself. "
"Similarly, when a price rule for a specific product is added to a pricelist, "
"it is also reflected on the product form via the :guilabel:`Extra Prices` "
"smart button."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:325
msgid ""
"The *Discounts* feature allows the ability to set a discount or increase the "
"price on *individual items* in a sales order. This is calculated as a "
"percentage of that product's sales price."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:328
msgid ""
"To access discounts, navigate to the *Sales* app setting page "
"(:menuselection:`Sales app --> Configuration --> Settings`), and click "
"the :guilabel:`Discounts` checkbox, then click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:None
msgid "Click the checkbox labeled Discounts to activate Discounts."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:335
msgid ""
"After the setting has been activated, navigate to the desired quotation by "
"going to :menuselection:`Sales app --> Orders --> Quotations` at the top of "
"the page. Once there, click on the desired quote from the list."
msgstr ""
"После активации настройки перейдите к нужному коммерческому предложению, "
"выбрав :menuselection:`Приложение Продажи --> Заказы --> Коммерческие "
"предложения` в верхней части страницы. Там нажмите на нужное предложение из "
"списка."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:339
msgid ""
"In the order lines section of the quotation form, a new column heading will "
"appear labeled :guilabel:`Disc.%`. This column is used to set discounts on "
"individual line items. Enter the desired discount for each product line and "
"the new price will automatically be calculated in the "
"quote :guilabel:`Total` at the bottom of the page."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:345
msgid ""
"A discount can also be added directly to a sales order in the same way. "
"Navigate to :menuselection:`Sales app --> Orders --> Orders`, click on the "
"desired sales order, and add the discount to :guilabel:`Disc.%` as described "
"above."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:None
msgid "The Dis.% heading will now appear in Order Lines."
msgstr "Заголовок Скидка % теперь будет отображаться в строках заказа."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:353
msgid ""
"Positive values for :guilabel:`Disc.%` will apply a *discount*, while "
"negative values can be used to *increase* the price."
msgstr ""
"Положительные значения для :guilabel:`Скидка %` применят *скидку*, в то "
"время как отрицательные значения можно использовать для *увеличения* цены."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:359
msgid "Discount button"
msgstr "Кнопка скидки"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:361
msgid ""
"In Odoo 17, with the :ref:`Discounts setting <sales/discounts>` enabled, "
"a :guilabel:`Discount` button appears at the bottom of sales orders."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:None
msgid ""
"The discount button located at the bottom of a sales order form in the Odoo "
"Sales app."
msgstr ""
"Кнопка скидки, расположенная в нижней части формы заказа на продажу в "
"приложении Odoo Продажи."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:367
msgid ""
"When the :guilabel:`Discount` button on a sales order is clicked, "
"a :guilabel:`Discount` pop-up window appears."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:370
msgid ""
"On this pop-up window, configure the :guilabel:`Discount` percentage, and "
"select one of the following discount options: :guilabel:`On All Order "
"Lines`, :guilabel:`Global Discount`, or :guilabel:`Fixed Amount`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:374
msgid ""
":guilabel:`On All Order Lines`: When selected, Odoo provides the ability to "
"add the specified discount percentage (configured in "
"the :guilabel:`Discount` field of the pop-up window) on all existing order "
"lines of the sales order."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:377
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Global Discount`: When selected, Odoo adds a discount product to "
"the order, which has the cumulative value equivalent to the specified "
"discount percentage (configured in the :guilabel:`Discount` field of the pop-"
"up window). Any product added (or removed) *after* the discount is added "
"does **not** affect the discount value on the order line."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:383
msgid ""
"In this example, since the total of the order is $600, and there is a 30% "
"global discount, that specific line is added to the sales order with a -180 "
"value (which is 30% of $600)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:0
msgid ""
"The sales order with the applied global discount option in the Odoo Sales "
"application."
msgstr ""
"Заказ на продажу с примененной опцией общей скидки в приложении Odoo Продажи."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:389
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Fixed Amount`: When selected, the percentage designation in "
"the :guilabel:`Discount` field turns to a monetary value (e.g. dollars), "
"wherein a specific amount must be entered. This configured value is added as "
"a discount line on the sales order."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:394
msgid ""
"It is more beneficial to add a :guilabel:`Fixed Amount` discount after "
"**all** desired products have been added to a sales order. If there are "
"changes made to the sales order *after* the discount is added, make sure to "
"change the value on the :guilabel:`Discount` line, or remove the line and "
"add the discount again."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:404
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Advanced price rules (discounts, formulas)` pricelist feature "
"provides the option to set price change rules based on discounts and "
"formulas. These changes can be relative to the product list/catalog price, "
"the product's cost, or another pricelist."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:408
msgid ""
"To use advanced pricing rules, with discounts and formulas, select "
"the :guilabel:`Advanced price rules (discounts, formulas)` option, after "
"enabling the :guilabel:`Pricelists` feature on the *Sales* app setting page "
"(:menuselection:`Sales app --> Configuration --> Settings`), and "
"click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:413
msgid ""
"After activating and saving that :guilabel:`Pricelists` feature, "
"the :guilabel:`Settings` page reloads and, from here, either select "
"the :guilabel:`Pricelists` link (beneath the :guilabel:`Pricelists` feature "
"on the :guilabel:`Settings` page), or navigate to :menuselection:`Sales app "
"--> Products --> Pricelists`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:421
msgid ""
"From the :guilabel:`Pricelists` page, select a desired pricelist to modify, "
"or create a new pricelist by clicking the :guilabel:`New` button."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:424
msgid ""
"On the pricelist form, under the :guilabel:`Price Rules` tab, "
"click :guilabel:`Add a line` to add an advanced price rule. Doing so reveals "
"a :guilabel:`Create Pricelist Rules` pop-up form, in which the advanced rule "
"is configured."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:None
msgid "How the Create Pricelist Rules pop-up form looks in Odoo Sales."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:432
msgid "Price computation"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:434
msgid ""
"On this form, first choose one of the three :guilabel:`Computation` options:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:436
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Fixed Price`: the price computation is based on a fixed price."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:437
msgid ":guilabel:`Discount`: the price computation is based on a discount."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:438
msgid ":guilabel:`Formula`: the price computation is based on a formula."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:441
msgid ""
"Each :guilabel:`Computation` option reveals its own computation-specific "
"fields on the form."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:443
msgid ""
"If :guilabel:`Fixed Price` is selected, enter the desired price in "
"the :guilabel:`Fixed Price` field below. If :guilabel:`Discount` is "
"selected, enter the desired discount percentage in the :guilabel:`Discount` "
"field that appears."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:447
msgid ""
"If :guilabel:`Formula` is selected, a number of configurable options appear."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:None
msgid "The various formula computation options present in Odoo Sales."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:452
msgid ""
"To configure the :guilabel:`Formula` computation option, start by selecting "
"an option from the :guilabel:`Based on` field: :guilabel:`Sales "
"Price`, :guilabel:`Cost`, or :guilabel:`Other Pricelist`. This determines "
"what the advanced price rule formula will be based on."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:456
msgid ""
"Next, in the :guilabel:`Discount` field, determine how much of a discount "
"should be applied. It should be noted that a mark-up can be applied by "
"setting a negative discount in this field."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:460
msgid ""
"To formulate a 100% markup (or 2 times the cost of the product), with a $5 "
"minimum margin, set the :guilabel:`Based on` field to :guilabel:`Cost`, "
"the :guilabel:`Discount` to `-100`, and the :guilabel:`Margins` to `5`. This "
"is often seen in retail situations."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:0
msgid ""
"How it looks to formulate a markup cost with 5 dollar minimum margin in Odoo "
"Sales."
msgstr ""
"Как выглядит формулировка наценки с минимальной маржей в 5 долларов в Odoo "
"Продажи."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:467
msgid ""
"Then, in the :guilabel:`Extra Fee` field, specify a fixed amount to add (or "
"subtract) to the amount calculated with the discount. After that, enter a "
"desired figure in the :guilabel:`Rounding Method` field. The rounding method "
"sets the price so that it is a multiple of the value in the field."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:472
msgid "Rounding is applied *after* the discount and *before* the surcharge."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:475
msgid ""
"To have prices that end in 9.99, set the :guilabel:`Rounding Method` to `10` "
"and the :guilabel:`Extra Fee` to `-0.01`."
msgstr ""
"Чтобы цены оканчивались на 9.99, установите в поле :guilabel:`Метод "
"округления` значение `10`, а в поле :guilabel:`Дополнительный сбор` значение "
"`-0.01`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:478
msgid ""
"Lastly, specify the minimum amount of margin over the base price in "
"the :guilabel:`Margins` field."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:480
msgid ""
"Once all formula-related configurations are complete, Odoo provides an "
"example of the formula in a blue block to the right of the configurations."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:484
msgid ""
"To apply 20% discounts, with prices rounded up to 9.99, set "
"the :guilabel:`Based on` field to :guilabel:`Sales Price`, "
"the :guilabel:`Discount` field to `20`, the :guilabel:`Extra Fee` field to "
"`-0.01`, and the :guilabel:`Rounding Method` field to `10`."
msgstr ""
"Чтобы применить скидку 20% с округлением цен до 9.99, установите в поле "
":guilabel:`На основе` значение :guilabel:`Цена продажи`, в поле "
":guilabel:`Скидка` значение `20`, в поле :guilabel:`Дополнительный сбор` "
"значение `-0.01`, а в поле :guilabel:`Метод округления` значение `10`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:0
msgid "Example of a 20% discount with prices rounded to 9.99 in Odoo Sales."
msgstr "Пример скидки 20% с округлением цен до 9.99 в Odoo Продажи."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:492
msgid "Conditions"
msgstr "Условия"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:494
msgid ""
"At the bottom of the :guilabel:`Create Pricelist Rules` pop-up form is "
"the :guilabel:`Conditions` section."
msgstr ""
"В нижней части всплывающей формы :guilabel:`Создать правила прайс-листа` "
"находится раздел :guilabel:`Условия`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:497
msgid ""
"Here, start by selecting one of the options in the :guilabel:`Apply On` "
"field:"
msgstr ""
"Здесь сначала выберите один из вариантов в поле :guilabel:`Применить к`:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:499
msgid ""
":guilabel:`All Products`: the advanced pricelist rule will be applied to all "
"products."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Все товары`: расширенное правило прайс-листа будет применено ко "
"всем товарам."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:500
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Product Category`: the advanced pricelist rule will be applied to "
"a specific category of products."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Категория товаров`: расширенное правило прайс-листа будет "
"применено к определенной категории товаров."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:502
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Product`: the advanced pricelist rule will be applied to a "
"specific product."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Товар`: расширенное правило прайс-листа будет применено к "
"определенному товару."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:503
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Product Variant`: the advanced pricelist rule will be applied to "
"a specific product variant."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Вариант товара`: расширенное правило прайс-листа будет применено "
"к определенному варианту товара."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:506
msgid ""
"If any of those options, apart from :guilabel:`All Products`, are selected, "
"a new option-specific field appears, in which the "
"specific :guilabel:`Product Category`, :guilabel:`Product`, "
"or :guilabel:`Product Variant` must be chosen."
msgstr ""
"Если выбран любой из этих вариантов, кроме :guilabel:`Все товары`, "
"появляется новое поле, специфичное для варианта, в котором необходимо "
"выбрать конкретную :guilabel:`Категорию товаров`, :guilabel:`Товар` или "
":guilabel:`Вариант товара`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:510
msgid ""
"Then, select a minimum quantity to be applied to the advanced pricelist rule "
"in the :guilabel:`Min. Quantity` field. Lastly, select a range of dates for "
"the pricelist item validation in the :guilabel:`Validity` field."
msgstr ""
"Затем выберите минимальное количество для применения к расширенному правилу "
"прайс-листа в поле :guilabel:`Мин. количество`. Наконец, выберите диапазон "
"дат для проверки элемента прайс-листа в поле :guilabel:`Срок действия`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:514
msgid ""
"Once all configurations are complete, either click :guilabel:`Save & Close` "
"to save the advanced pricelist rule, or click :guilabel:`Save & New` to "
"immediately create another advanced pricelist rule on a fresh form."
msgstr ""
"После завершения всех настроек либо нажмите :guilabel:`Сохранить и закрыть`, "
"чтобы сохранить расширенное правило прайс-листа, либо нажмите "
":guilabel:`Сохранить и создать`, чтобы немедленно создать другое расширенное "
"правило прайс-листа в новой форме."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing.rst:519
msgid ""
"If a price rule is set for a particular product, and another one for its "
"product category, Odoo takes the rule of the product itself."
msgstr ""
"Если правило цены установлено для конкретного товара, а другое — для его "
"категории товаров, Odoo применяет правило самого товара."

